Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}片名：大白鲨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.53,0:02:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你叫什么名字来着？ - 克莉丝{\r}\N[ Boy ] What's your name again ? Chrissie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 我们到哪去？ - 游泳{\r}\NWhere we goin' ? Swimming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}慢一点{\r}\NSlow up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.11,0:02:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别跑这么快{\r}\NSlow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.28,0:02:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我没醉呀，慢点！{\r}\NI'm not drunk. Slow down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.92,0:02:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}等等 我来了{\r}\NWait! I'm coming. I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.76,0:02:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我真的追上来了！{\r}\NI'm definitely coming. [ Giggling ]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.63,0:02:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}停一下！{\r}\NWhoa ! Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.61,0:03:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我会游泳{\r}\NI can swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}却不会走路 也不会脱衣服！{\r}\NI just can't walk or undress myself. [ Chuckling ]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.06,0:03:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快下水呀！{\r}\NCome on in the water !
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别急！{\r}\NTake it easy. Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}救我！{\r}\NHelp me !
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.65,0:04:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我来了！我来了！{\r}\N[ Whispering ] I'm coming. I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.09,0:04:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好痛！{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.99,0:04:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}天呀！{\r}\NOh, my God !
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}天呀！{\r}\NOh, God !
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.67,0:04:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}天呀！不要！{\r}\NOh, God, no ! God, no !
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.84,0:04:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}上帝救救我{\r}\NPlease help !
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.03,0:05:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[ Radio ] Local fishing reported good...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}艾米提租船提早开放{\r}\Nand many boat rental yards opening early...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.73,0:05:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}准备迎接旺季{\r}\Nto prepare for the annual seasonal rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我是威斯{\r}\NThis is W-I-S-S-- [ Groaning ]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}为什么此地总不出太阳？{\r}\N[ Man ] How come the sun didn't use to shine in here ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们秋天买的房子{\r}\NWe bought the house in the fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.05,0:05:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}现在是夏天{\r}\Nand this is summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.59,0:05:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}去喂喂狗吧{\r}\NSomebody feed the dogs, huh ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.45,0:05:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好的{\r}\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.53,0:05:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}看到孩子了吗？{\r}\NDo you see the kids ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[ Radio ] ... forecast calls for clear skies and fair weather...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.20,0:05:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at least through the regatta weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}一定是跑到后院去了{\r}\NThey must be in the backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}在艾米提通常说“后院儿”{\r}\NIn Amity you say ''yahd.''
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.77,0:05:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们在“后院儿” 离“车儿”不“远儿”{\r}\NThey're in the ''yahd,'' Not too ''farh'' from the ''carh.''
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.11,0:06:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 怎么样？ - 倒像是纽约客{\r}\NHow's that ? Like you're from New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.02,0:06:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}妈，我流血了 刚刚被吸血鬼咬到{\r}\NMom, I got cut. I got hit by a vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.39,0:06:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们又去打秋千了{\r}\NYou guys were playin' on those swings. [ Phone Ringing ]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那个秋千很危险 千万别去很危险，我还没修好{\r}\NThose swings are dangerous. Stay off there. Yuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.66,0:06:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}还不至于死 这种小伤口算不了什么{\r}\N[ Dial Tone ] I think you're gonna live. Hello. It's not the biggest thing I've ever seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 是的 - 我可以游泳吗？{\r}\NYeah. Can I go swimmin' ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.57,0:06:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}可以，但先等我把伤口处理好{\r}\NYeah, but let me clean this first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你通常都怎么做 洗掉还是冲掉{\r}\NWhat do they usually do, wash up or float or what ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.41,0:06:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you don't go past the jetty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不K留在原地{\r}\NOh, no, no, no. Keep 'em there. I'll be out...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我一刻钟K 到二十分钟内赶到，好吗？{\r}\Nin about fifteen, twenty minutes, all right ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Get a Band-Aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.59,0:06:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我得走了，有人失踪{\r}\N[ Man ] Gotta go... missing person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}游泳季还不到 根本都还没有人来{\r}\NSeason hasn't started. Nobody's even here yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.20,0:06:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}警长，你给我听着 小心点好吗？{\r}\NListen, Chief,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.53,0:06:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 这个小镇！不必了 - 爹地{\r}\Nbe careful, will ya ? In this town ? Hey. Bye, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“艾米提警局” 等我上去！{\r}\NWait. Let me get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.74,0:06:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 把杯子还我 - 没问题{\r}\NI want my cup back ! You'll get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.58,0:07:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}再见{\r}\NWave good-bye. Bye !
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For folks at the beaches, we've got some safety tips for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.63,0:07:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The safety council says --
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.00,0:07:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“欢迎光临艾米提岛”{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.67,0:07:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没人见到她下水？{\r}\NAnd nobody saw her go into the water ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.11,0:07:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}可能有 我当时昏昏沉沉的{\r}\NSomebody could've. I was sort of passed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.85,0:07:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你的意思是她跑开了 - 不是{\r}\NYou mean, she ran out on you ? No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.75,0:07:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}她一定是淹死的{\r}\NShe must've drowned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.99,0:07:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}总之是我向你报的案对吗？{\r}\NLook, I reported it to you, didn't I ?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.56,0:07:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你住在这里？ - 不是！住在哈特佛{\r}\NYou live here ? No, Hartford.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.49,0:07:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我念三一学院 家人住在格尼屈{\r}\NI go to Trinity. My folks live in Greenwich.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:07:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你家人在这出生的？ - 没错，但我是外岛人{\r}\NYour folks were born here ? Yeah, I'm an islander.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:08:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}家父退休后 他们才搬来{\r}\NThey moved off when my dad retired.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.93,0:08:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你也是本岛人吗？ - 不是，纽约人{\r}\NYou an islander ? No, New York City.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.27,0:08:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你是来渡暑假的？{\r}\NYou here for the summer ?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快走{\r}\NC'mon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.45,0:08:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}老天K{\r}\NHold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}老天{\r}\N[ Chief Brody ] Oh, Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你今儿个可来的真早{\r}\NWell, you're up awful early !
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}警长在里面吗？{\r}\NIs the chief in there ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}警长，你忙什么？{\r}\NWell, Chief, what have you got on ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.90,0:09:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}波莉，若你想工作进行顺利{\r}\NPolly, if this filing system is going to work,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.97,0:09:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}必须把那些旧公文拿走{\r}\Nkeep outdated stuff off my desk;
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.97,0:09:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 只在桌上放“急件”行吗？ - 是的，警长{\r}\Njust the pending. Yes, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.04,0:09:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}很多人打电话来抱怨 那家空手道学校{\r}\NWe've got a bunch of calls about that karate school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那个学校九岁的学生{\r}\NIt seems the nine year olds from the school... [ Buzzing ]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.68,0:09:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}劈栏杆来练功{\r}\Nare ''karating'' the picket fences.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.35,0:09:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}布洛迪警长办公室 是验尸官打来的{\r}\NChief Brody's office. The medical inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.33,0:09:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“鲨鱼食人”{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.76,0:09:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}消防队长要你去讨论国庆日K{\r}\NThe fire chief wants you to go over the 4th of July --
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}帮我列一张全市{\r}\NI want a list of all the water activities...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.10,0:09:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}水上活动的清册{\r}\Nthat the city fathers are planning for today. Right away ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}韩瑞克 “海滩关闭”的告示牌放哪？{\r}\NHendricks, where do we keep the ''beach closed'' signs ? Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.21,0:09:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}从来没有{\r}\NWe never had any. No ?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.91,0:09:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我店前有一辆卡车 载满了破盘子{\r}\NThere's a dead truck smack in front of my store.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}叫他先填一份表格{\r}\N[ Brody ] Just have him fill out the form.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.12,0:09:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}先填好再说{\r}\NJust fill it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.21,0:10:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你看那些孩子 把我的围墙弄成什么样子{\r}\NLook what the kids did to my fence. Eight or nine year olds. Hey, glasses, huh ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 是的，眼镜？ - 下午再给你电话{\r}\NYeah, glasses. Can I call you this afternoon ?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.82,0:10:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我向你保证{\r}\NI'll call you in the afternoon, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“艾米提岛欢庆七月四日”{\r}\N[ Whistle ]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这一些货到八月都不能卖{\r}\NThis stuff isn't gonna help me in August.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}玩水的人都在六月来{\r}\NThe summer ginks come down here in June.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.19,0:10:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我订的货你一样也没有{\r}\NYou haven't got one thing on here I ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.93,0:10:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没有遮阳伞 没有躺椅，没有海滩球{\r}\NNot a beach umbrella, sun lounger, beach balls --
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}如果你们服务再K{\r}\NIf I can't get service --
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.11,0:10:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}警长！{\r}\NChief !
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.68,0:11:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}波莉派我来找你 她说有一批童子军{\r}\NChief, Polly sent me to find you... to tell you there's a bunch of boy scouts in Avril Bay...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.11,0:11:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}在艾佛湾举行游泳比赛{\r}\Ndoin' their mile swim for their merit badges.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.28,0:11:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我联络不上 那儿没电话{\r}\NI couldn't call them in. There's no phones out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好吧，你下车{\r}\NOkay, c'mon, get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.72,0:11:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}把这些拿回办公室 做一些告示牌{\r}\NTake this stuff to the office and get to work on those signs. All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“海滩关闭，禁止游泳 艾米提警局”{\r}\N''Beaches closed, no swimming by order of the Amity P.D.''
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.46,0:11:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 让波莉去上油漆 - 为什么不让我漆？{\r}\NLet Polly do the printing. What's the matter with my printing ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.93,0:11:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}让波莉漆{\r}\NLet Polly do the printing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}警长！{\r}\NHey, Chief? Chief Brody !
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.27,0:11:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}市长，今早南滩有人 被鲨鱼咬死了{\r}\NWhat have you got there ? We had a shark attack at South Beach this morning, Mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.74,0:11:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我得去封闭海滩{\r}\NFatal ! I've got to batten down the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.81,0:11:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}艾尔柏，快呀 笨蛋{\r}\NOkay, Albert, Come on, you kook.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.95,0:11:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}手臂抬高点{\r}\NKeep your arms up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.95,0:11:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fight it. Let it carry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.62,0:11:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}查理！带我到孩子那边{\r}\NCharlie, take me out to those kids, will ya ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.48,0:12:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}马丁{\r}\NMartin ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你想下令把海滩封闭掉？{\r}\NYou gonna shut down the beaches on your own authority ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}莫非还需要别人的命令？{\r}\NWhat other authority do I need ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.49,0:12:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}技术上，你需要颁订市民法 或是专人表决通过{\r}\NTechnically you need a civic ordinance or resolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这一套都是照章行事{\r}\NThat's just going by the book.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们其实对你这样仓促行事 有点顾虑{\r}\NWe're anxious that you're rushing into something serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.36,0:12:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这是你上任的第一个夏天{\r}\NIt's your first summer, you know ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.20,0:12:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这句话什么意思？{\r}\NWhat does that mean ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我真正的意思是 艾米提是个避暑胜地{\r}\NI'm only trying to say that Amity is a summer town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.70,0:12:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们需要赚这笔钱{\r}\NWe need summer dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.94,0:12:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}如果这儿不准人游泳{\r}\NIf the people can't swim here, they'll be glad to swim...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}游客会跑到鳕鱼角 新汉普顿或长岛{\r}\Nat the beaches of Cape Cod, the Hamptons, Long Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.95,0:12:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}也不能冒被鲨鱼咬的危险呀{\r}\NThat doesn't mean we serve them a smorgasbord.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.01,0:12:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}本海域中未曾出现过这种麻烦{\r}\NWe never had that kind of trouble in these waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.52,0:12:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那个女孩又是被什么咬死的？{\r}\NWhat else could have done that to that girl ? Boat propeller ?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.59,0:12:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 船的螺旋桨？ - 我认为K可能是{\r}\NI think possibly, yes, a boating accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 没错，划船出了意外 - 你电话上可不是这么对我说的{\r}\NThat's not what you told me over the phone. I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.76,0:12:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我弄错了 报告书上也得修改{\r}\NWe'll have to amend our reports.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.13,0:12:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你坚持这种说法？ - 我坚持{\r}\NYou'll stand by that ? I'll stand by that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.97,0:13:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}只不过是个女生{\r}\NOh -- Martin... a summer girl 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.60,0:13:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}在海中游远了、累了 渔船开过来K{\r}\Ngoes swimming, swims out a little far.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}以前也发生过{\r}\NShe tires, a fishing boat comes along -- It's happened before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.11,0:13:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我认为你并不了解 一般人对这种事情的反应{\r}\NI don't think you appreciate the gut reaction people have to these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.24,0:13:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}哈利，我了解 我只是照听到的事实采取措施{\r}\NI appreciate it. I'm just reacting to what I was told.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.45,0:13:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}马丁，群众心里都一样{\r}\NMartin, it's all psychological.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.72,0:13:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你大喊“梭鱼”{\r}\NYou yell ''barracuda'' ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.89,0:13:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}其他人就问“什么？”{\r}\Nand everybody says, ''Huh ? What ?''
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.39,0:13:24.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你若喊出“鲨鱼”{\r}\NYou yell ''shark,''
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.39,0:13:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}今年国庆日就满城人心惶惶{\r}\Nwe've got a panic on our hands on the 4th of July.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.30,0:13:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好了，送我们回去吧{\r}\NOkay, you can take us back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.58,0:13:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我要拿救生筏再下水{\r}\NI'm gonna get my raft and go back out in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.12,0:13:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我看看你的手指{\r}\NLet me see your fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.09,0:13:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}亚力克金特纳 你的手指都泡白了{\r}\NAlex Kintner, they're beginning to prune.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.32,0:13:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}再让我去玩一下子{\r}\NJust a little longer ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.49,0:13:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 再十分钟 - 谢谢{\r}\NJust ten more minutes. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.53,0:14:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没有岛民 他们都不是岛民{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.83,0:14:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}真烦{\r}\N[ Woman ] All I want to know--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.00,0:14:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我只想知道一件小事 我什么时候才能成为岛民？{\r}\NI want to know one, simple thing. When do I get to become an islander ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.17,0:14:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}艾琳，别想{\r}\NEllen, never !
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你不是在此出生 就不是岛民{\r}\NYou're not born here, you're not an islander.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.90,0:15:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别去烦他 马上回来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.84,0:15:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}马丁，我知道 你在镇上也有一些问题要处理{\r}\NHey, Marty, I know you got a lot of problems downtown,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.87,0:15:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不过我家里也出问题 希望你能来处理{\r}\Nbut I got problems at the house I wish you could take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.58,0:15:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}第一件事 我家门口有一堆猫赖着不走{\r}\NI've got cats parking in front of the house --
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}还有在办公室旁边的垃圾车{\r}\N[ Screaming ]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我没法去上班{\r}\NAnd that garbage truck next to the office has got to be moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.39,0:15:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}因此我想弄一块禁停区 这种事你很容易处理{\r}\NI need a red zone. It's a simple thing you could take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.05,0:15:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 之前你做过 - 甜心，请你过来一下好吗？{\r}\NHoney, would you come here a minute, please ? Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.80,0:15:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你没事吧？{\r}\NAre you okay ?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.50,0:15:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}很好！好K{\r}\NYeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是不是小孩子下水 令你担心了{\r}\NIf the kids goin' in the water is worrying you --
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.10,0:15:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}可以叫他们到沙滩上来玩呀{\r}\NNo, no. They can play out here on the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.34,0:15:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没关系，让他们去{\r}\NIt's all right. Let them go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.88,0:16:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好冷{\r}\NIt's cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.39,0:16:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们了解你，警长{\r}\NWe know all about you, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你从不下水吗？{\r}\NYou don't go in the water at all, do you ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.29,0:16:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你那顶帽子真丑，哈利{\r}\NThat's some bad hat, Harry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.43,0:16:21.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}布洛迪警长，你太紧张了{\r}\NChief Brody, you are uptight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}放松点{\r}\NC'mon... 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对呀{\r}\Nthat's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon. [ Yelling And Laughing ]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你认识松饼小子？ - 提比！{\r}\N# Oh, do you know the muffin man #
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.28,0:16:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 松饼小子喜欢杜瑞莲 - 提比！{\r}\N# The muffin man The muffin man # Pippet !
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.52,0:16:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}提比！{\r}\NPippet !
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.86,0:16:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}回来呀，提比！{\r}\NPippet ! C'mon, Pippet !
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}提比！{\r}\NPippet!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.65,0:17:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你看见了吗？ - 看见了{\r}\NDid you see that ? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.23,0:17:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}血！{\r}\N[ Yelling ]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.63,0:17:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}统统上来！{\r}\NGet everybody out ! Get out !
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.34,0:17:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快上来！{\r}\NGet them out !
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}麦克，上来！{\r}\NMichael, get out of the water !
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.79,0:17:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[ Man ] Take it easy. It's gonna be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.43,0:17:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}亚力克{\r}\NAlex ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.73,0:17:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be okay, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.07,0:18:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}亚力克{\r}\NAlex ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.64,0:18:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“若有能力猎杀该鲨鱼 赏金三千重酬K”{\r}\N[ Man ] Alex Kintner is the kid who was missing at the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}根本不确定是否有鲨鱼{\r}\NWe don't even know that there's a shark around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我无法跟你争辩 也无法跟你谈{\r}\NI can't argue with you. I can't talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.85,0:18:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't argue with you. I can't talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我要跟金特纳太太谈谈 这已经变成竞赛了{\r}\NI've got to talk to Mrs. Kintner because this is going to turn into a contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.32,0:18:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}还不只这份“公告” 她还登报悬赏{\r}\NIt's not just the Gazette. She's advertised in out-of-town papers.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.39,0:18:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}大家都会知道这件事{\r}\NPeople all over New England are gonna know about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.03,0:18:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}到会议室，空间比较大{\r}\NLet's go to council chambers where we'll have more room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我负责这里的安全问题{\r}\NI'm responsible for public safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.54,0:18:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那你明天再去看 免得有人受伤{\r}\NThen go see that no one gets hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.27,0:18:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 马丁，你想个办法K - 这只是件小事{\r}\NMarty, do something about this. It's a small story.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.34,0:18:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我尽可能小做 登在杂货广告栏上{\r}\NI'm gonna bury it as deep as I can... in back with the grocery ads.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.41,0:18:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}请进来{\r}\NRight in here, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.85,0:18:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}请进{\r}\NMove on in, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.72,0:19:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.33,0:19:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我不明白你为何 要这样小题大做？{\r}\NWhy do you insist on playing the heavy all the time ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.73,0:19:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你听着，我的看法 能代表本镇大多数人{\r}\NI have a point of view and it speaks for many of the people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.31,0:19:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}并不是因为我有汽车旅馆 你觉得如何？{\r}\NIt's not only me. How do you feel ? I hope they don't close beaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.41,0:19:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 我希望别关海滩 - 请安静{\r}\NLet's have some order.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}请各位安静{\r}\NLet's have order, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.42,0:19:25.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}有什么特别的问题吗？{\r}\NAny special questions ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.09,0:19:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那三千悬赏是现金还是支票？{\r}\NIs that $3000 bounty on the shark in cash or check ? [ Laughing ]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.82,0:19:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我一点也不觉得 这有什么好笑的{\r}\NI don't think that's funny at all. I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.33,0:19:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这件事是渔人 和金特纳太太间的私事{\r}\NAll right. All right ! That's private business between you fishermen and Mrs. Kintner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.37,0:19:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}马丁，请你移驾？ 布洛迪警长{\r}\NMartin ? Would you, please ? Chief Brody.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.31,0:19:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我想宣布目前的计划{\r}\NI want to tell you what we're planning so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}海滩怎么处理？{\r}\NWhat about the beaches ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.41,0:19:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们尽快找几位 暑期副警长来协助{\r}\NWe're gonna put on the extra summer deputies as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.95,0:20:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}然后在海滩上派员监视{\r}\NThen we're gonna try and use shark spotters on the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你要不要关闭海滩？{\r}\NAre you going to close the beaches ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.46,0:20:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是的，要关闭{\r}\NYes, we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.83,0:20:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们同时打算由本土K{\r}\NWe're planning to bring in some experts
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}请海洋研究机构来此{\r}\N from the oceanographic institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.70,0:20:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}只关闭二十四小时{\r}\NOnly 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.84,0:20:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我可没有同意{\r}\NI didn't agree to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.94,0:20:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}只关闭二十四小时{\r}\NOnly 24 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.81,0:20:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}二十四小时等于三星期这么久{\r}\N2 4 hours is like three weeks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们都认识我{\r}\NYou all know me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}知道我靠什么维生{\r}\Nknow how I earn a livin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:21:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我亲自去抓那头鲨鱼 不过问题没那么容易{\r}\NI'll catch this bird for you, but it ain't gonna be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.15,0:21:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是条恶鱼{\r}\NBad fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.18,0:21:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不比到池塘抓鳕鱼{\r}\NNot like goin' down to the pond and chasin' bluegills or tommy-cods.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.49,0:21:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这条鲨鱼可以吞掉一个人{\r}\NThis shark, swallow you whole.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.92,0:21:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}只要转转舌头，咽个口水{\r}\NA little shakin', a little tenderizin',
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.59,0:21:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}人就进肚了{\r}\Ndown you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.43,0:21:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们的动作得快 别把观光客吓跑{\r}\NAnd we gotta do it quick. Gotta bring back the tourists.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.33,0:21:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}让生意正常经营{\r}\NThat'll put all your businesses on a payin' basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.40,0:21:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这样做不太容易{\r}\NBut it's not gonna be pleasant !
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.77,0:21:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我估计我这条命 绝不只三千美金{\r}\NI value my neck a lot more than three thousand bucks, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.71,0:21:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}找到它三千{\r}\NI'll find him for three,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.44,0:21:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但抓到要宰，就得要一万{\r}\Nbut I'll catch him and kill him for ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.88,0:21:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们得下决心{\r}\NYou gotta make up your minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.42,0:21:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}想要过好日子就得拿出钱来{\r}\NGonna stay alive and ante up, or gonna play it cheap ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.42,0:21:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}否则出手太小气 整个冬天就得看天过日子{\r}\NBe on welfare the whole winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.46,0:21:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我不要有志愿者 也不要有人同行{\r}\NI don't want no volunteers, no mates.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.96,0:21:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这么小的岛上，到处都是船长{\r}\NThere's too many captains on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.60,0:21:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}一万元美金我要自己独吃{\r}\N$ 1 0,000 for me, by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我负责把鲨鱼头、鲨鱼尾{\r}\NFor that you get the head,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.74,0:21:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}交出来{\r}\Nthe tail, the whole damn thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.34,0:22:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}非常谢谢你，昆特先生{\r}\NThank you very much, Mr. Quint.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.98,0:22:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们会再商量一下{\r}\NWe'll take it under advisement.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.85,0:22:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}市长先生，警长{\r}\NMr. Mayor... Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.76,0:22:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}各位先生女士失陪了{\r}\NLadies and gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.07,0:22:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“不准游泳 艾米提警局关闭海滩”{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.24,0:22:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“鲨鱼”{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.68,0:22:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“微波”{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.28,0:22:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“侦测系统”{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.69,0:22:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}天呀，你吓坏我了{\r}\NOh, God ! You scared me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.69,0:22:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.40,0:23:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}艾琳，一般人都不了解鲨鱼{\r}\NYou know, Ellen, people don't even know how old sharks are.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.13,0:23:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们往往活二、三千年之久{\r}\NI mean, if they live two, three thousand years. Martin ?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.67,0:23:07.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 他们不知道 - 够了{\r}\NThey don't know ! Enough, enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.44,0:23:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}今晚恐怕你都睡不着了{\r}\NYou're not gonna be able to sleep tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.48,0:23:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 喝吧 - 谢了{\r}\NHere, c'mon. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.22,0:23:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}想不想喝个醉胡闹一番？{\r}\NWanna get drunk and fool around ?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.52,0:23:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}想呀{\r}\NOh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.00,0:23:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}麦克真是喜欢他的礼物{\r}\NHey, Mikey really loves his present.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.60,0:23:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他在哪？{\r}\NWhere is he ?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.24,0:23:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}坐在礼物里面{\r}\NSitting in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.17,0:23:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}老天爷！{\r}\NGood God !
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.61,0:23:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好了，麦克 快上来！{\r}\NAll right, Michael, out of the boat !
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.68,0:23:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}船绑在防波堤上 我坐在船上{\r}\NTied up to the jetty, sittin' in the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.35,0:23:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快来帮麦克{\r}\NHelpin' Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.92,0:23:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 快上来！ - 爹，再让我多玩一会！{\r}\NGet out of that boat ! Hi, Dad. Just a little longer, please ?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.62,0:24:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 明天就是他生日 - 我不准他在海里{\r}\NIt's his birthday tomorrow. I don't want him on the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.96,0:24:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他没在海里，他在船上 他又不会下水{\r}\NHe's not on the ocean. He's in a boat. He's not gonna go in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.20,0:24:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}昨天的事发生过后 他怎敢下水{\r}\NI don't think he'll ever go in the water again after what happened yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.10,0:24:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别这么说{\r}\NAll right, now don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.77,0:24:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我不希望发生那种事 你也知道{\r}\NI don't want that to happen, you know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.11,0:24:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我要他先看看划船的规定方法{\r}\NBut I want him to read the boating regulations, the rules,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.21,0:24:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}免得他冒冒失失的就去划船{\r}\Nbefore he goes out on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.11,0:24:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}麦克，你有没有听到你爹的话？{\r}\NMichael, did you hear your father ?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.22,0:24:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}现在就上来！快上来！{\r}\NOut of the water, now ! Now !
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.13,0:24:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我有点累了，先休息一下 免得有人去报警{\r}\NI'm tired. Let's stop before someone reports us.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.33,0:24:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别担心！警长住在岛的另一边{\r}\NDon't worry. The chief lives on the other side of the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.17,0:24:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我划的方向是直的吗？{\r}\NAm I comin' in straight ?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.57,0:24:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别担心，继续划{\r}\NJust keep rowin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.02,0:24:58.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}保佑咱们别空手而归 这是我太太假日要吃的牛肉{\r}\N[ Man ] We'd better catch somethin'. This is my wife's holiday roast.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.09,0:25:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别愁了！ 三千元美金可以买不少牛肉{\r}\NDon't worry about it. $3000 buys an awful lot of roast.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.10,0:25:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快来吃吧！{\r}\NCome and get it !
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.87,0:25:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}会被潮水带到外海{\r}\NThe tide's takin' it right out.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.34,0:25:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们先回家吧{\r}\NCan't we go home ?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.53,0:26:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}嘿！它咬走了{\r}\NHey. Hey, he's takin' it ! He's takin' it ! - He's takin'it. - Hey, go ! Go !
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.31,0:26:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}咬走了！{\r}\NGo, go, go !
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.77,0:27:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}查理，听我的话 别往后看！{\r}\NCharlie, take my word for it ! Don't look back !
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.57,0:27:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快游呀，查理，快呀！{\r}\NSwim, Charlie, swim ! C'mon, Charlie, swim !
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.38,0:27:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}游呀，查理，加油！{\r}\NSwim, Charlie, c'mon, to me, boy! C'mon, Charlie, swim to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.15,0:27:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}加油！{\r}\NC'mon, keep swimmin'. Keep swimmin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.28,0:27:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}查理，快游呀！{\r}\NC'mon, a little more. Atta boy! Atta boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.52,0:27:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我爬不上来{\r}\N[ Charlie ] I can't get up ! I can't get up !
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.79,0:27:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}手给我！{\r}\NGive me your hand. C'mon. I can't get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.49,0:27:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}帮我！{\r}\NHelp me !
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.43,0:27:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}脚上来！快点！{\r}\NHelp me ! Get your feet outta the water! Get your feet up. Atta boy! Atta boy, Charlie.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.08,0:27:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}可以回家了吧{\r}\NCan we go home now ?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.38,0:27:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“艾米提海港港务局长”{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.39,0:27:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[ Hendricks ] Then Denherder and Charlie sat there...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.79,0:27:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}然后丹贺德和查理 坐在那儿喘气{\r}\N[ Hendricks ] Then Denherder and Charlie sat there... tryin' to catch their breath, figurin' out how to tell Charlie's wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.33,0:27:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}盘算怎么和查理的太太 交代冰箱里的牛肉{\r}\Nwhat happened to her freezer full of meat.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.30,0:27:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这不好笑{\r}\NThat's not funny at all !
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.87,0:28:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}金特纳太太一定在 “野外”杂志上登广告了{\r}\NMrs. Kintner must have put her ad in Field and Stream.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.77,0:28:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我看来倒像是“国家讯报”{\r}\NLooks more like the National Enquirer.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.27,0:28:07.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}一点道理也没有 我一直想理性点{\r}\N[ Arguing ]
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.74,0:28:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}停！{\r}\NAll right, hold it ! Just hold it !
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.65,0:28:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 哈！ - 哈，小伙子，你好{\r}\NHello. Hello back, young feller. How are you ?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.95,0:28:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你该不会和 那些疯子一起出海吧？{\r}\NI hope you're not going out with those nuts, are you ?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.89,0:28:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}韦塔的船先移开 否则他出不来{\r}\NThe Weetock boat's gotta move out first. You have to move out or he can't get out at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.93,0:28:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}先别张帆，先收起来{\r}\NAhoy ! Don't raise sail. You're just gonna luff it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.93,0:28:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 船上有桨吗？ - 有{\r}\NYou got a paddle ? Scull it out of here. Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.50,0:28:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}划出去 警官，等一下K{\r}\NOfficer, wait a second. Wait. Just--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.44,0:28:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}嘿，你们有多少人坐那条船？{\r}\NHey, how many guys you gonna put aboard that boat ?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.08,0:28:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 只要安全就行了对吗？ - 那样根本不安全！{\r}\NWhatever's safe, right ? Well, that ain't safe !
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.61,0:28:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}小心点，那是炸药{\r}\NHey, watch it. That's dynamite.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.78,0:28:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}等一下！你想带着去哪？{\r}\NWait a minute. Where are you going with that ?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.39,0:28:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 我要上船呀 - 不行，不行{\r}\NI'm goin' on the boat. Oh, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.72,0:28:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}拜托一下 帮我叫那些人下船好吗{\r}\NHelp me get those guys out of the boat, will you ?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.12,0:28:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}可以{\r}\NSure.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.32,0:29:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}各位先生{\r}\NGentlemen, the officer asked me to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.69,0:29:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}警官要我转告你们，船超载了{\r}\Nthat you're overloading that boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.83,0:29:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}走开！{\r}\NAh, get out of here. Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.37,0:29:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你别管闲事行吗 你在乎个什么劲{\r}\NYou ain't going! What do you care ? Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.50,0:29:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你可以告诉我岛上 有没有好的餐厅或旅馆{\r}\NCan you tell me if there's a restaurant or hotel on the island ?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.70,0:29:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}一直往前走就有{\r}\NYeah, you walk straight ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.94,0:29:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们统统会死{\r}\N[ Laughing ] Ha-ha-ha. They're all gonna die.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.38,0:29:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}波莉你听我说 外面有些路障告示牌{\r}\NPolly, listen. We've got roadblock signs outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.91,0:29:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你去找人帮忙{\r}\NYou gotta get somebody to help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.92,0:29:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}把告示牌搬到公路上面去{\r}\NGet those roadblock signs out on the highway,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.72,0:29:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}因为来玩得游客太多了 应付不了{\r}\Nbecause we got more people down here than we can handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.62,0:29:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 什么事？ - 你在那里干嘛？{\r}\N- Yeah ? - What are you doing ?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.89,0:29:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 他们都是你的人，去跟他们谈 - 他们不是，全是来自各州的游客{\r}\NThese are your people. Go and talk to them. Those aren't my people !
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.43,0:29:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你有没看到停车场里的车牌？{\r}\NThey're from all over. Did you see the license plates ?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.43,0:29:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}康乃狄克，罗德岛，纽泽西 外面就我一人张罗{\r}\NConnecticut, Rhode Island, New Jersey.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.03,0:29:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不是有人来支援吗？{\r}\NWhat happened to the extra help we're supposed to get ?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.77,0:29:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}在国庆日前就只有你跟我两人{\r}\NThat's not 'til the 4th of July. Until then, it's you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.40,0:29:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你知道那艘船上的八个人吗？{\r}\NYou know those eight guys on the fantail launch ? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.84,0:29:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们一个也别想活着上岸{\r}\NNone of them are gonna get out of the harbor alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.44,0:29:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我就是和你谈这个问题 你认识他们，快去谈{\r}\NThat's what I'm talkin' about. You know their first names. Talk to those clowns !
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.15,0:29:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}今天每个人好像都很开心{\r}\NEveryone seems to be having a good time today. Tell me about it !
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.82,0:29:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 波莉，我再回电话给你 - 那里能找到布洛迪警长？{\r}\NI'll get back to you. Could you tell me how I could find chief Brody ?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.25,0:30:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你是谁？ - 麦特胡柏{\r}\NWho are you ? Matt Hooper. 
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.69,0:30:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}海洋研究学院派来的{\r}\NI'm from the oceanographic institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.52,0:30:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}老天爷！我们就是找你{\r}\NOh, for Christ sakes. You're the guy we called.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.73,0:30:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 我就是布洛迪 - 幸会！{\r}\NI'm Brody. Oh, I'm very glad to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.13,0:30:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 幸会！ - 我知道你目前很忙{\r}\NI'm glad to meet you too. I know you got a lot on your hands now, but --
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.56,0:30:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}有何事需要效劳的？{\r}\NWhat can we do for you ?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.23,0:30:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我想先看看死者的肢体{\r}\NI think the best thing for me to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.34,0:30:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 那位海滩上的女孩？ - 好的，跟我一块来{\r}\Nis to see the remains of the first victim, the girl on the beach. Okay, fine,Just bear with me. Thanks. Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.88,0:30:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}等我们把那些小混帐 赶到海岩堆上时{\r}\NWait'll we get them silly bastards down in that rock pile.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.21,0:30:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们会后悔自己的老爹 娶了自己的老妈{\r}\NThey'll wish their fathers had never met their mothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.38,0:30:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}到时再看看他们伤着心 从石头中挖尸体吧{\r}\Nwhen they start diggin' their bottoms out and slammin' into them rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.75,0:30:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快点回去！该死的傻瓜{\r}\N[ Man ] Get away from there, you goddamn fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.26,0:30:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们是怎么回事？ 专门给我们找麻烦{\r}\NWhat's the matter with you ? You wanna swamp us you crazy son-of-a-bitch ?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.76,0:30:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你们干什么？ - 那些人在干什么？{\r}\NWhat are you doin' ? What are these guys doin' out here ?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.36,0:30:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}告诉我们，他们在干嘛？{\r}\NWhat the hell they doin' ?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.43,0:30:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 他们在放饵 - 这算哪门子事？{\r}\NThey're chummin' right now.Chumming ? What the hell is that ?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.93,0:30:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们在吸引鲨鱼{\r}\NThey're tracking the shark.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.44,0:30:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}三千元除以四是多少？{\r}\N$3000 divided four ways is what ?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.41,0:31:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}让胡柏先生看看那名受害者{\r}\NLet's show Mr. Hooper our accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.09,0:31:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}受害者名叫克莉丝华肯斯{\r}\N''Victim identified as Christine Watkins, female Caucasian.''
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.19,0:31:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 白种人女性 - 这是我们调查的结果{\r}\NHere's the way we have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.79,0:31:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 可能是撞船事件 - 对{\r}\N''Probable boating accident.'' Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.46,0:31:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好吗？{\r}\NAll right ?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.03,0:31:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}死者的高度和体重{\r}\NThe height and weight of the victim...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.17,0:31:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}只能由其部份残肢中预估{\r}\Ncan only be estimated from the partial remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.17,0:31:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[ Breathing Deeply ]
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.04,0:31:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}躯干由胸腔部份分割成段{\r}\NThe torso has been severed in mid-thorax, no major organs remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.71,0:31:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}内脏器官都没有留下 可以给我杯水吗？{\r}\NMay I have a glass of water ?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.78,0:31:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}右臂被咬断{\r}\NThe right arm has been severed above the elbow,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.05,0:31:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}上肘处大肌块不见{\r}\Nwith massive tissue loss in the upper musculature.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.96,0:31:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}谢谢{\r}\NThank you, very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.56,0:31:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}部份无肌骨骼残存 这不是船只意外造成的{\r}\NPartially denuded bone remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.40,0:31:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你有没有通知海岸巡逻队？{\r}\NThis was no boat accident. Did you notify the Coast Guard about this ?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.43,0:31:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没有，这种事管辖权属于本县{\r}\NNo, it was only local jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.01,0:32:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}左臂、头、肩膀、胸骨 肋骨都已断裂{\r}\NThe left arm, head, shoulders, sternum and portions of the rib cage are intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.74,0:32:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不要抽烟！谢谢你{\r}\NDo not smoke in here !
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.08,0:32:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}情形就是如此{\r}\NThis is what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.35,0:32:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}情况显示{\r}\NIt indicates the non-frenzied feeding of a large squalus,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.45,0:32:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}大型巨齿动物{\r}\Npossibly Longimanus or Isurus glauca.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.49,0:32:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}大块肌肉不见，影响了K{\r}\NNow... the enormous amount of tissue loss...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.89,0:32:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}细部分析工作{\r}\Nprevents any detailed analysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.80,0:32:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不过攻击的巨齿动物{\r}\NHowever, the attacking squalus must be considerably larger...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.23,0:32:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}显然比海中任何动物体型都大{\r}\Nthan any normal squalus found in these waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.54,0:32:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你有没下水去查看过海域？{\r}\NDidn't you get out a boat and check out these waters ? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.07,0:32:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这根本不是船只意外！{\r}\N[ Hooper ] This is not a boat accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.24,0:32:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}既不是螺旋桨，也不是暗礁{\r}\NIt wasn't any propeller. It wasn't any coral reef.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.88,0:32:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}更不是杀人狂{\r}\NAnd it wasn't Jack the Ripper !
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.95,0:32:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是鲨鱼{\r}\NIt was a shark.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.96,0:32:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们带回来的{\r}\N[ Man ] You heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.83,0:32:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我要照张照片{\r}\NWe brought it home!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.93,0:33:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}新闻送到美联社和合众社 先在本州刊出{\r}\NListen, I wanna go AP and UPI. I wanna get on the state wire services.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.51,0:33:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}然后交由波士顿方面 做全国版刊登{\r}\NSee if Boston'll pick it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.64,0:33:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}通知纽约的戴夫艾斯拉 转告他欠我一次人情{\r}\NCall Dave Axelrod. Tell him he owes me a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.71,0:33:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我要拍一张全体合照 鱼也包括在里面好吗{\r}\NThis is the shot I want with everybody and the fish in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.78,0:33:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}请各位集合一下{\r}\N[ Reporter ] Can we please get organized?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.42,0:33:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我要拍一张新闻照{\r}\NI wanna get a picture for the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.75,0:33:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 请各位K - 是班加德纳抓的？{\r}\NBen Gardner get this ?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.42,0:33:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不是，我们抓的{\r}\N[ Man ] No, no, no. We caught it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.69,0:33:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}恭喜{\r}\NWe got it. We got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.96,0:33:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}谢谢{\r}\NHey, that's swell. That's a beauty, ain't it ?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.46,0:33:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我要拍一张新闻照 请各位别挡路{\r}\N[ Reporter ] I need a picture for the paper. Clear out of the way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.43,0:33:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我只拍抓到鲨鱼的人 请别挡着好吗？{\r}\NJust the guys who caught the fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.60,0:33:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我要拍渔人和鲨鱼的合照{\r}\NCould you open it up a little, please ?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.07,0:33:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我要拍张新闻照 请你把告示牌举起来{\r}\NC'mon, guys, please. I need a picture for the paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.81,0:33:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could we get the ''beach closed'' sign ?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.78,0:33:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 我要你站这边 - 不是我抓的{\r}\N[ Indistinct ]
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.98,0:33:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}蹲下，像高中一样 一脚蹲着，一脚往前{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.62,0:33:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}走开{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.25,0:33:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}年轻人，请你出去好吗？{\r}\NYoung fellow, could you step out of the picture ?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.52,0:33:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}把东西一起拿走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.79,0:34:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 我们准备好了 - 谢谢你{\r}\NGet real. We're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.79,0:34:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}请你拍一张好吗？{\r}\N- Can you get that, please ?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.40,0:34:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 怎么样？ - 钱呢？{\r}\N- How's that ?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.67,0:34:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}告诉市长拿钱去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.83,0:34:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}赖利！{\r}\NLarry !
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.94,0:34:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}赖利！你不会相信的{\r}\NLarry, you won't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.81,0:34:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这是什么鲨？{\r}\NWhat kind of a shark is it ? I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.77,0:34:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不知道！依我看是灰鲨 好深的喉咙{\r}\NI think it's a mako. It's got a deep throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.61,0:34:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但它究竟是哪一种鲨鱼？{\r}\N- Yeah, but what kind of shark ?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.51,0:34:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}虎鲨{\r}\N- Tiger shark.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.45,0:34:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你说什么？{\r}\NA what ?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.15,0:34:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}总算松口气了 班可拍了不少新闻照{\r}\NWe can start breathing again.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.15,0:34:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这还用说{\r}\NBen getting plenty of pictures ? You bet he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.22,0:34:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你说什么口径不够大？ - 这张嘴可真大{\r}\NWhat is this ''bite radius'' crap ? That is a big mouth !
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.33,0:34:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没人阻止你把头插进去 你自己看看它会不会吃人{\r}\NStuff your head in there and find out if it's a man-eater !
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.47,0:34:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我是说有可能不是{\r}\NAll I'm saying is that it may not be the shark.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.70,0:34:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 口径不对 - 我为你介绍麦特{\r}\NIt's just a slight -- Matt ?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.21,0:34:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 我不想被打 - 这位是赖利彭恩市长{\r}\NThis is Larry Vaughn, our mayor. Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.31,0:34:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}麦特是海洋研究学院派来的{\r}\NMatt's from the oceanographic institute. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.54,0:34:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}真令人兴奋，市长？{\r}\NTerrific, huh, Mayor ?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.25,0:34:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}马丁，海中有很多种类的鲨鱼{\r}\NMartin, there are all kinds of sharks in the waters;
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.85,0:35:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}榔头鲨、白头鲨 蓝鄂鲨、虎鲨K{\r}\Nhammerheads, white tips, blues, makos.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.45,0:35:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那些人抓的鲨鱼，很可能是K{\r}\NThe chances these bozos got the exact shark --
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.72,0:35:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}海里这种鲨鱼可是很少见{\r}\NThere's no other shark like this in these waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.22,0:35:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}马丁，百分之一{\r}\NIt's a hundred to one... a hundred to one.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.73,0:35:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我不否定是这条鲨鱼 也许是{\r}\NI'm not saying this is not the shark. It probably is.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.06,0:35:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}海中很少见食人鲨{\r}\NIt's a man-eater. It's extremely rare for these waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.83,0:35:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}该鲨鱼的口径{\r}\NBut the fact is that the bite radius on this animal...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.24,0:35:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}与死者身上的伤口不符{\r}\Nis different than the wounds on the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.51,0:35:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我想要再确定 你也希望如此{\r}\NI just -- I wanna be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.18,0:35:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们都这样希望，是吗？ 我要做一个简单的实验{\r}\NYou wanna be sure. We all wanna be sure, okay ? What I want to do is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.28,0:35:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}鲨鱼的消化过程相当缓慢 我们先把鱼肚剖开{\r}\NThe digestive system of this animal is very slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.62,0:35:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}它在二十四小时之内吃的东西 一定还留在胃内{\r}\NWhatever it's eaten in the last 24 hours is bound to still be in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.92,0:35:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}然后我们就可以确定了{\r}\NThen we'll be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.93,0:35:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}要弄清楚只有这个法子{\r}\NIt may be the only way to confirm it, huh ?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.10,0:35:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}先生！头脑弄清楚{\r}\NLook, fellas, let's be reasonable, huh ?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.93,0:35:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}此时此地{\r}\NThis is not the time or place to perform ...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.40,0:35:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不适合你表演解剖技术{\r}\Nsome kind of half-assed autopsy on a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.81,0:35:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我也不会站在这里{\r}\NI'm not going to stand here and see that thing cut open...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.98,0:36:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}眼睁睁的看着那个孩子的尸体 满地都是！{\r}\Nand see that Kintner boy spill out all over the dock !
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.36,0:36:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}警长{\r}\NChief Brody ? Yes ?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.94,0:36:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我刚才知道{\r}\NI just found out...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.18,0:36:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}有个女孩子上星期死在海里{\r}\Nthat a girl got killed here last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.25,0:36:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}而你早就知道{\r}\NAnd you knew it !
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.95,0:36:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你明明知道海里有鲨鱼{\r}\NYou knew there was a shark out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.82,0:36:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你明明知道有危险性{\r}\NYou knew it was dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.96,0:36:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}而你却不阻止大伙去游泳{\r}\NBut you let people go swimming anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.03,0:36:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这些事情你早就知道了{\r}\NYou knew all those things,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.23,0:37:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}而我儿子已经死了{\r}\Nbut still my boy is dead now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.41,0:37:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你都无能为力{\r}\NAnd there's nothing you can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.98,0:37:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我儿子已经死了{\r}\NMy boy is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.23,0:37:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我要你知道这件事{\r}\NI wanted you to know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.81,0:37:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对不起，马丁！她错了{\r}\NI'm sorry, Martin. She's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.78,0:37:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}她没错{\r}\NNo, she's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.65,0:37:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好了，各位{\r}\N[ Vaughn ] All right, fellas,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.49,0:37:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快把这只狗杂碎割下来 免得弄得全海滩臭气冲天{\r}\Nlet's cut this ugly son-of-a-bitch down... before it stinks up the whole island.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.96,0:37:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}哈维，你和卡尔 明天把它丢掉{\r}\NHarve, you and Carl take it out tomorrow and dump it in the drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.63,0:39:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}过来一下{\r}\NCome here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.34,0:39:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}吻我一下{\r}\NGive us a kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.41,0:39:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}为什么？{\r}\NWhy ?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.41,0:39:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}因为我想要{\r}\NBecause I need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.58,0:39:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 哈？ - 你走吧{\r}\NHello. Get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.15,0:39:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 有什么事吗？ - 我可以进去吗？{\r}\N[ Ellen ] Can I help you ? Mind if I come in ?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.55,0:39:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 我是麦特胡柏 - 嗨，我是艾琳布洛迪{\r}\NI'm Matt Hooper. Hi. Ellen Brody.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.62,0:39:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你先生在家？ 我很希望和他谈谈{\r}\NYour husband's home ? I'd like to talk to him. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.39,0:39:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是的，我也想{\r}\NYes, so would I.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.56,0:39:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}请进，要不要喝杯咖啡？{\r}\NCome in. Can I get you some coffee ? No, nothing, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.67,0:39:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 不，谢谢 - 有酒呀！真好{\r}\NOh, wine. How nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.69,0:40:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你今天还好吗？{\r}\NHow was your day ?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.16,0:40:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好极了{\r}\NSwell.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.83,0:40:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是{\r}\NYeah. I got red and white.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.53,0:40:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我带了红、白各一瓶 不知道你喜欢哪一种 太好了{\r}\NI didn't know what you'd be serving. Oh, that's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.21,0:40:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这个有人吃吗？{\r}\NIs anyone eating this ?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.07,0:40:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没有{\r}\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.68,0:40:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我先生说你专研究鲨鱼{\r}\NMy husband tells me you're in sharks.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.25,0:40:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对不起，是的 不过我没听别人这样子说法{\r}\N[ Hooper Laughing ] Excuse me, well, yes. I've never heard it quite put that way,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.19,0:40:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}的确是如此！我爱鲨鱼{\r}\Nbut yes, I am. I love sharks.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.26,0:40:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你爱鲨鱼？ - 是的，我爱鲨鱼{\r}\NYou love sharks. Yeah, I love them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.33,0:40:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我十二岁那年 父亲送我一艘船{\r}\NWhen I was twelve, my father got me this boat 
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.50,0:40:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我到鳕鱼角钓鱼{\r}\Nand I went fishing off Cape Cod.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.57,0:40:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我要鲷鱼做饵 一下子就钓了{\r}\NI hooked a scup and as I was reeling it in,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.64,0:40:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}一条四英尺半的小鲨鱼{\r}\NI hooked a 4-and-a-half foot baby thresher shark, who proceeded to eat my boat. [ Laughing ]
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.44,0:41:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他咬我的船，还有水上救生衣{\r}\NHe ate my oar, hooks, and my seat cushions.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.05,0:41:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}把我从船上挤下了海 我吓得半死{\r}\NHe turned an inboard into an outboard. Scared me to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.22,0:41:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}拼命游上岸去{\r}\NAnd I swam back to shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.19,0:41:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}到了海滩之后，转过头一看{\r}\NWhen I was on the beach, I turned around...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.52,0:41:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我的船已经被咬成两半{\r}\Nand actually saw my boat being taken apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.72,0:41:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}自从那件事之后 我就开始研究鲨鱼{\r}\NEver since then, yes, I have been studying sharks.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.29,0:41:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}所以我了解 我明天要飞回研究所去{\r}\NThat's why I know that I'm going to go to the institute tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:18.00,0:41:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}告诉他们此地有鲨鱼问题{\r}\Nand tell them that you still have a shark problem here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.73,0:41:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你为何要告诉他们？ - 抱歉{\r}\NWhy do you have to tell them that ? Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.47,0:41:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你不是说已经 把鲨鱼抓起来了吗？{\r}\NI'm sorry. You told me the shark was caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.97,0:41:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我在新闻广播上也听到 岛角电台说的{\r}\NI heard it on the news, on the cape station.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.54,0:41:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他们是抓了一条鲨鱼 但不是那条鲨鱼{\r}\NThey caught a shark, not the shark.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.74,0:41:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不是咬死克莉丝那一条{\r}\NNot the shark that killed Chrissie Watkins;
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.95,0:41:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}可能也不是咬死小男孩的那一条{\r}\Nand probably not the shark that killed the little boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.42,0:41:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我本来想解剖鲨鱼来证明K{\r}\Nwhich I wanted to prove by cutting the shark open.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.88,0:41:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别倒那么多K 算了，没关系{\r}\NYou want to let that breath -- ? Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.60,0:41:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好{\r}\NYeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.97,0:42:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你知道{\r}\NYou know, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.77,0:42:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}明天我一走 全岛就剩下你一个明智的人了{\r}\Nyou're gonna be the only rational man left after I leave tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.34,0:42:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你要去哪里？{\r}\NWhere you going ? Ahh.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.58,0:42:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我要去欧罗拉{\r}\NI'm going on the Aurora.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.42,0:42:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}欧罗拉是什么？{\r}\NWhat is that ?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.95,0:42:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是一座海上避难所 患了鲨瘾的人去的地方{\r}\NIt's a floating asylum for shark addicts.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.92,0:42:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}纯粹做研究工作 在海上已经十八个月了{\r}\NPure research... 1 8 months at sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.02,0:42:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}马丁讨厌船{\r}\NMartin hates boats.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.66,0:42:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}马丁讨厌海水{\r}\NMartin hates water. Martin --
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.59,0:42:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们搭渡船到本土时 他都坐在车内{\r}\NMartin sits in his car when we go on the ferry to the mainland.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.93,0:42:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我想是和小时候有关 医学上有个名称不是吗？{\r}\NI guess it's a childhood thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.27,0:42:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}惧溺症{\r}\NThere's a clinical name for it. Drowning.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.84,0:42:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}据说大多数的人是在水深3英尺处{\r}\NIs it true that most people get attacked by sharks...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.74,0:42:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}离岸10英尺远，遭鲨鱼攻击 是真的吗？{\r}\Nin 3 feet of water, about 1 0 feet from the beach ?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.08,0:42:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是的{\r}\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.84,0:42:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}人在下海游泳 做为消遣之前{\r}\NAnd before people started to swim for recreation,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.18,0:42:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}就有很多鲨鱼攻击事件{\r}\NI mean, before sharks knew what they were missing,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.35,0:42:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}只不过是没有记录而已{\r}\Nthat a lot of these attacks weren't reported ?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.46,0:42:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没错{\r}\NThat's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.36,0:42:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 那条独来独往的鲨鱼 - 恶棍{\r}\NNow, this shark that swims alone -- Rogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.79,0:42:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}恶棍？是的{\r}\NWhat's it called ? Rogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.36,0:43:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}它本来在一个食物充足{\r}\NNow this guy, he keeps swimming around in a place...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.03,0:43:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}的海域游泳 直到食物溃乏的时候，对吗？{\r}\Nwhere the feeding is good until the food supply is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.10,0:43:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这叫做领域性{\r}\NThat's called territoriality.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.17,0:43:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我很同意这种理论{\r}\NIt's a theory that I happen to agree with.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.44,0:43:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那我们再喝一杯之后 就去把鲨鱼肚子剖开{\r}\NWhy don't we have one more drink and go down and cut that shark open ?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.58,0:43:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你能做到吗？{\r}\NMartin ? Can you do that ?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.12,0:43:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我什么都能做，我是警长呀{\r}\NI can do anything. I'm the chief of police.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.10,0:43:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们先由食道开始{\r}\NWe start in the alimentary canal...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.24,0:43:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}把胃袋给剖开{\r}\Nand open the digestive tract.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.47,0:44:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 正如我所料的 - 什么？{\r}\NAgh ! Just like I thought ! What ?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.67,0:44:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是由南方的海域中{\r}\NCame up from the gulf stream,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.77,0:44:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}随着暖流游来的{\r}\Nfrom southern waters.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.85,0:44:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“路易西安那”{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.38,0:44:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 它该不会吃汽车吧？ - 不，虎鲨像垃圾桶{\r}\NHe didn't eat a car, did he ? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.85,0:44:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}无所不吃 也许是人由河中倒入的{\r}\NA tiger shark's like a garbage can. It'll eat anything. Somebody probably threw that in the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.40,0:44:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}就只有这些{\r}\NThat's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.50,0:44:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我得通知市长，关闭海滩{\r}\NI've got to close the beach, call the mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.50,0:44:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}另外那条更麻烦{\r}\NYou've got a bigger problem than that, Martin.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.84,0:44:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}海中还有一条更大的{\r}\NYou've still got a hell of a fish out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.34,0:44:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}嘴巴至少有这么大{\r}\Nwith a mouth about this big.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.11,0:44:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}明早我怎么说服大家？{\r}\NHow do we confirm that by morning ?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.92,0:45:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}如果它是恶棍 如果领域性是真的{\r}\NIf he is a rogue and there's any truth to territoriality at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.45,0:45:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们便可在南滩 和史考特岬角之间找到它{\r}\Nwe've got a good chance of spotting him between Cape Scott and South Beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.49,0:45:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你去哪？ - 我现在就去找它{\r}\NWhere you going ? I'm gonna find him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.49,0:45:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 它是夜食者 - 你要出海？{\r}\NHe's a night feeder.On the water ?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.29,0:45:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}难道在陆地上找得到鲨鱼吗？{\r}\NWe're not gonna find him on land.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.36,0:45:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 但我也不会醉得坐小船去 - 你得去{\r}\NI'm not drunk enough to go out on a boat ! Yes, you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.37,0:45:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 不去 - 要去{\r}\NNo, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.83,0:45:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 我做不到 - 你能{\r}\NI can't do that ! Yes, you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.64,0:45:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}纽约的犯罪率真惊人{\r}\NThe crime rate in New York will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.91,0:45:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}问题层出不穷 让人有一种无力感{\r}\NThere are so many problems, you never feel like you're accomplishing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.25,0:45:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}抢劫，杀人{\r}\NViolence, rip-offs, muggings.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.29,0:45:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}孩子不能离家，上学得有人陪{\r}\NKids can't leave the house. You gotta walk 'em to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.76,0:45:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但在艾米提镇上情况就不同了{\r}\NBut in Amity, one man can make a difference !
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.33,0:45:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}二十五年以来 从未发生过凶杀案{\r}\NIn 25 years, there's never been a shooting or murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.47,0:45:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}真好！想不想吃脆饼？{\r}\NMartin, want a pretzel ?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.34,0:45:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这是什么地方？{\r}\NWhere are we ?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.77,0:45:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}就在鲨鱼猎食的地方{\r}\NWe're right in the stretch where he's been feeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.81,0:46:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这玩意晚上能看节目吗？{\r}\NCan you get the late show on this thing ?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.31,0:46:06.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不行，这是闭路电视 船头船尾各放一架摄影机{\r}\NNo, it's a closed-circuit TV system. I have underwater cameras fore-and-aft.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.15,0:46:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这些玩意都是谁花钱买的？ 政府还是研究院{\r}\NWho pays for all this stuff? The government, an institute ?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.15,0:46:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这玩意花不少钱{\r}\NThis stuff costs a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.99,0:46:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}大部分都是我自己买的{\r}\NWell, I pay for this mostly myself, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.03,0:46:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}开玩笑{\r}\NYou're kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.43,0:46:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没有{\r}\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.70,0:46:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你有钱？ - 是的{\r}\NYou rich ? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.16,0:46:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}多有钱？{\r}\NYeah ? How much ?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.53,0:46:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你指我个人还是家族？{\r}\NPersonally or the whole family ?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.64,0:46:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这种说法不合逻辑{\r}\NDoesn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.17,0:46:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}家人会花钱买这东西 让你去看鲨鱼？{\r}\NThey pay a guy like you to watch sharks ?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.21,0:46:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对一个讨厌海的人{\r}\NWell, uh --
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.58,0:46:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}住在岛上也不合情理{\r}\NIt doesn't make much sense for a guy who hates water to live on an island, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.08,0:46:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}从海上看才觉得这是座岛{\r}\NIt's only an island if you look at it from the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.08,0:46:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这么说的确有些道理{\r}\NThat makes a lot of sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.29,0:46:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那玩意是干什么的？{\r}\N[ Beeping ] [ Martin ] What is that thing doing ?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.43,0:46:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那是追踪鱼用的{\r}\NIt's a fish finder.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.30,0:46:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}可能是一群鲭鱼之类的{\r}\NIt's probably a school of mackerel all clumped together.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.97,0:46:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}等一下{\r}\NWait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.21,0:47:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 还有别的东西 - 是什么？{\r}\NThere's something else out there. What is it ?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.81,0:47:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}在南西南一百码处{\r}\NAbout a hundred yards, south southwest.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.78,0:47:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}班加德纳的船{\r}\N[ Brody ] That's Ben Gardner's boat ! You know him ?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.45,0:47:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你认识他？ - 当然认识，他是渔人{\r}\NIt's all banged up. Sure, I know him. He's a fisherman.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.09,0:47:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}怎么回事？{\r}\NWhat happened ?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.00,0:48:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}马丁，我得过去查查看{\r}\NMartin, I've got to go down and check their hull.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.23,0:48:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 我们把船拉过来再说好了 - 我会的，但我得先检查一下{\r}\NWhy don't we tow it all in ? We will.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.30,0:48:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}往船上照{\r}\NI've got to check something out. Get the lines for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.33,0:48:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}拖过来算了{\r}\NLet's tow it in.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.77,0:48:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别担心，不会出事的{\r}\NDon't worry. Nothin's gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.71,0:48:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你不在的时候我怎么办？{\r}\NWhat am I supposed to do while you're gone ?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.78,0:48:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}什么事也别做{\r}\NNothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.98,0:48:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}什么事也别做{\r}\Nabsolutely nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.58,0:48:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别碰任何仪器{\r}\NDon't touch any of the equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.42,0:48:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}两分钟后就回来{\r}\NI'll be back in two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.24,0:50:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是一条大白鲨{\r}\NThis is a great white, a big one !
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.41,0:50:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}任何鲨鱼专家都会说 它是杀人凶手，食人兽{\r}\NAny shark expert in the world will tell you it's a killer, a man-eater !
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.21,0:50:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}大白鲨已艾米提岛附近{\r}\NThe situation is, that apparently a great white shark...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.11,0:50:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}做为它活动领域{\r}\Nhas staked a claim in the waters off Amity Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.75,0:50:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}只要海中还有食物 它就会继续在此地出没{\r}\NHe's going to continue to feed here as long as there is food in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.79,0:50:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}很难预料它会怎么做{\r}\NThere's no limit to what he's gonna do.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.52,0:50:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}已经发生过三次意外 一星期之内二人丧生{\r}\NWe've had 3 incidents, two people killed in a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.19,0:50:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这种事还会再有 以前就发生过了，纽泽西海滩{\r}\NIt happened before.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.43,0:50:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 在1916年 - 共有五个人冲浪时被咬死{\r}\NThe Jersey beach, 1 91 6, Five people chewed up in the surf.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.93,0:50:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 前后一星期 - 你告诉他游泳的事{\r}\NTell him about the swimmers.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.03,0:50:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}鲨鱼会受到某种拨水声 或活动的吸引前来{\r}\NA shark is attracted to the exact kind of splashing that occurs...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.07,0:50:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}游泳时一定会发生{\r}\Nwhenever human beings go in swimming. You cannot avoid it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.14,0:50:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}如果你在国庆日开放海水浴场{\r}\NIf you open the beaches on the 4th of July,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.14,0:50:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}就等于摇铃开饭一样{\r}\N it's like ringing the dinner bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.01,0:50:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}彭恩先生{\r}\NMr. Vaughn, I pulled a tooth the size of a shot glass...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.44,0:51:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我在船壳上拔出一颗 玻璃碎片般大的鲨牙{\r}\Nout of the wrecked hull of a boat out there, the tooth of a great white.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.68,0:51:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 就是大白鲨的牙齿 - 船是班加德纳的，全被咬烂了{\r}\NIt was Ben Gardner's boat. It was all chewed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.88,0:51:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我帮忙拖回来的 你真该看看才对！{\r}\NYou should've seen it !
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.95,0:51:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}牙齿在哪？ 你见过吗，布洛迪？{\r}\NWhere is that tooth ? Did you see it, Brody ?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.79,0:51:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 我没见过，他回来时掉了 - 我跌了一跤{\r}\NNo, he dropped it -- I had an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.73,0:51:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你说鲨鱼叫什么名字来着？{\r}\NWhat did you say the name of this shark is ?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.16,0:51:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是巨鲨中的巨鲨 叫做大白鲨{\r}\NIt's a Carcharodon carcharias, a great white.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.93,0:51:24.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但你没拿牙齿回来{\r}\NBut you don't have the tooth ?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.57,0:51:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们镇上的收入全靠观光客{\r}\NWe depend on the summer people for our very lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.41,0:51:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你不会有K - 如果你关闭海滩{\r}\NYou're not gonna have a summer unless you deal with this problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.21,0:51:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们不仅要关闭浴场 还得雇人来杀鲨鱼{\r}\NWe're gonna have to hire somebody to kill the shark !
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.78,0:51:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们得通知海岸巡逻队{\r}\NWe're gonna have to tell the Coast Guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.88,0:51:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你得跟鲨鱼研究所联络{\r}\NYou'll have to contact the shark research panel.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.68,0:51:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 我们需要更多代表 - 你要警告整个港口K{\r}\NEvery nut in the world is gonna come in here !
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.92,0:51:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 我们要花钱K - 你们都不了解K{\r}\NI don't think either one of you
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.99,0:51:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这个问题的所在{\r}\Nare familiar with our problems !
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.66,0:51:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}依我看如果鲨鱼不咬你的话{\r}\NI'm familiar with the fact tha
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.89,0:51:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你根本不会{\r}\Nt you are going to ignore this particular problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.20,0:51:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}重视这个问题{\r}\Nuntil it swims up and bites you on the ass !
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.53,0:51:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}等一下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.03,0:51:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这问题有两种解决方法{\r}\NThere are two ways to deal with this problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.07,0:51:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}一者是把鲨鱼给杀了 一者是切断它的食物源{\r}\NYou're either gonna kill this animal or cut off its food supply.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.67,0:52:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们非关闭浴场不可{\r}\NWe have to close the beaches!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.04,0:52:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}布洛迪，病态的粗俗文化 “救命！鲨鱼！”{\r}\NBrody, sick vandalism !
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.58,0:52:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这简直刻意地混淆了大众视听{\r}\NThat is a deliberate mutilation of a public service message.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:10.05,0:52:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我要你把那些划匠抓起来{\r}\NI want those paint-happy bastards caught 
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.98,0:52:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}吊死{\r}\Nand hung up by their Buster Browns !
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.15,0:52:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}可以了，再见{\r}\NThat's it. I'm not gonna waste my time arguing with a man...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.52,0:52:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我可不想浪费时间 和一个将要当鲨鱼午餐的人胡扯{\r}\Nwho's lining up to be a hot lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.96,0:52:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}请你别这么做{\r}\NSee you later, buddy. Don't do this !
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.80,0:52:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}市长先生{\r}\NMr. Vaughn,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.33,0:52:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们面对的是一具巨型的{\r}\Nwhat we are dealing with is a perfect engine,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.27,0:52:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}食人机器 这真是进化的奇迹{\r}\Nan eating machine. It's a miracle of evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.47,0:52:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这种机器整天只会游泳{\r}\NAll this machine does is swim, eat,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.74,0:52:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}吃人 并制造小鲨鱼，如此而已{\r}\Nand make little sharks, and that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.51,0:52:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你为什么不仔细瞧瞧这个招牌？{\r}\NTake a long, close look at this sign.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.62,0:52:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 这些东西的比例倒是正确的 - 你就是喜欢求证炫耀{\r}\NThose proportions are correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.89,0:52:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}想登上国家地理杂志？{\r}\NLove to prove that, wouldn't you ? Get your name into the National Geographic ?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.27,0:53:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}如果我们现在就想办法 八月份还来得及开放{\r}\N[ Brody ] If we make an effort today, we might be able to save August.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.67,0:53:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}八月？{\r}\NAugust ? 
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.47,0:53:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}拜托你！明天就是国庆日{\r}\NFor Christ sake, tomorrow's the 4th of July !
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.88,0:53:13.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们要开放营业{\r}\NAnd we will be open for business,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.88,0:53:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}从来没有一个这么好的夏天{\r}\N one of the best summers we've ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.88,0:53:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}如果你们关心浴场的事 你们尽量让游客安全{\r}\NIf you fellas are concerned about the beaches, do whatever you have to to make them safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.98,0:53:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但浴场非在周末开放不可{\r}\NBut those beaches will be open for this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.44,0:53:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“载客处”{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.01,0:53:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你告诉我准备派多少人手给我？{\r}\NI wanna know how many men you're gonna send me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.08,0:53:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我没有理由去布里斯本{\r}\NDoctor, there is no need for me to come to Brisbane...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.38,0:53:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}此地就出现一条大白鲨{\r}\Nwhen I have a great white shark right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.42,0:53:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}此地需要人来保护游泳区{\r}\N[ Brody ] We need men to patrol the swimming area.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.69,0:53:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}有枪有船的人我们都用得到{\r}\NWe've gotta have help, anybody with a gun or boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.40,0:54:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}星期一？{\r}\NMonday !
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.70,0:54:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}密西根只适合看白老鼠{\r}\NIs Chief Petty Officer Feldman there ? What ? Dad !
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.84,0:54:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}什么？就是那留平头的小个子{\r}\NHe's the little guy with the crew cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.46,0:54:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}接线生，岛上有电话吗？{\r}\NOperator, isn't there a phone on the island ?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.53,0:54:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}请帮我接好吗？{\r}\NCould you connect me ?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.74,0:54:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快！杀死它！{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.44,0:54:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[ Brody ] I'm over at the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.61,0:54:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}布洛迪呼叫葛加 你听到了吗？{\r}\NBrody to ''Gotcha. '' Do you read me ?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.18,0:55:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}本土电视的史考特来了{\r}\NThose guys from the TV station on the mainland is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.52,0:55:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好的，我待会去找他{\r}\NAll right. I'll get to them later.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.66,0:55:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}布洛迪呼叫史卡巴，请回答{\r}\NBrody to ''Scutbucket.'' Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.87,0:55:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}布洛迪呼叫戴西 你听到了吗？{\r}\NBrody to ''Daisy.'' Do you read me ?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.50,0:55:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}美妙的旋律 你听到了吗？请回答，完毕{\r}\N[ Brody ] ''Fascinatin'Rhythm, '' do you read me ?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.97,0:55:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你看到什么状况？ - 什么也没看到，马丁{\r}\NCome in, Hooper. What do you see ?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.54,0:55:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}声纳上也没消息{\r}\NNothing here, Martin, and nothing on sonar.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.08,0:55:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}艾米提岛素以空气清晰 海水洁净{\r}\NAmity Island has long been known for its clean air,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.05,0:55:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}和美丽的白沙滩闻名全国{\r}\Nclear water, beautiful white sand beaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.78,0:55:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}然而近日来 这个美丽的避暑胜地上{\r}\NBut in recent days,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.75,0:55:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}笼罩着一片阴影{\r}\Na cloud has appeared on the horizon of this beautiful resort community,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.75,0:55:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}人人恐惧着一条食人的大白鲨{\r}\Na cloud in the shape of a killer shark.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.79,0:55:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}露天体育场办得很好 外面湿气很重{\r}\N[ Radio ] This stadium does hold the water well... and it is very soggy in the outfield.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.30,0:55:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}二坏一好 跑者在一三垒{\r}\NTwo balls, one strike, runners at first and third. Here's the pitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.97,0:55:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}打击出去 飞跃球，左外野{\r}\NFly ball, deep left field.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.98,0:55:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}泰瑞回来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.71,0:56:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}警告跑到，靠近墙边 出界{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.58,0:56:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}三垒被刺杀，他进来K{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.15,0:56:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 赖利 - 你怎么没下水？{\r}\NOh, hi, Larry. Why aren't you in the water ?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.09,0:56:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我刚擦了防晒油 我想晒一点K{\r}\NWell, I just put some suntan lotion on...
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.09,0:56:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没人下海呀{\r}\Nand I'm trying to absorb-- Nobody's going in.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.20,0:56:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}拜托你下去玩玩{\r}\NPlease, get in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.16,0:57:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}麦克，你来一下{\r}\NMike, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.43,0:57:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 麦克，帮我个忙好吗？ - 什么？{\r}\NListen, Mike, do me a favor, will ya ?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.50,0:57:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你和别人带着船到湾里 去玩好吗？{\r}\NWhat ? Take the boat and put it in the pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.97,0:57:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}水湾是给老太太玩的{\r}\NPond's for old ladies. I know it's for old ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.80,0:57:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我知道是老太太玩的 就算你帮老爸的忙{\r}\NJust do it for the old man, huh ?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.37,0:57:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}怎么样，拜托？{\r}\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.71,0:57:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好吧{\r}\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:39.38,0:57:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}谢谢{\r}\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.19,0:57:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我看着乔了{\r}\N[ Whispering ] I've got Sean.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.50,0:58:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}麦克，等等！{\r}\NMichael... wait ! Michael, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.87,0:58:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}麦克，我不喜欢你{\r}\NMichael, I don't like you no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.14,0:58:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[ Children ] Hey you! Throw it here! Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.21,0:58:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我能忍受哈利 情人{\r}\NI can stand Harry. You know, hey there, lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.83,0:58:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}戴西，我是韩力克{\r}\NDaisy, Daisy, this is Hendricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.16,0:58:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你有状况吗？ 我看到一个黑影{\r}\NAnything ? Thought I saw a shadow. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.53,0:58:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}韩力克，我是戴西 虚惊一场，我没看到任何异状{\r}\N[ Radio ] Hendricks, this is Daisy, I don't see anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.34,0:58:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}警报错误，可能是反光{\r}\NFalse alarm, must be this glare.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.09,0:58:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我很高兴有此机会 再一次强调{\r}\NI'm pleased and happy to repeat the news...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.39,0:59:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们已经将 咬伤游客的大鱼给杀死了{\r}\Nthat we have caught and killed a large predator... that supposedly injured some bathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.39,0:59:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}各位看，今天天气很好{\r}\NIt's a beautiful day, the beaches are open...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.40,0:59:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}浴场也开放 游客都玩得很开心{\r}\Nand people are having a wonderful time.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.63,0:59:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}众人皆知，艾米提 热诚地欢迎所有人{\r}\NAmity, as you know, means friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.71,0:59:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我的K{\r}\NMy... 
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.22,0:59:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}天呀！{\r}\NGod !
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.09,0:59:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}老天！ 鲨鱼鳍出水了！350方位{\r}\NJesus Christ ! Fin ! Shark ! Three-five-zero ! [ Radio ] We've got something here, something big.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.16,0:59:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}紧急呼叫！{\r}\NGet in there as fast as you can. Red one ! Red one !
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.80,0:59:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快把游客叫上岸 鲨鱼进海湾了{\r}\N[ Radio ] Get your people out. There's a shark in the bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.97,0:59:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别吹哨子！别吹哨子！{\r}\N- Everybody out of the water! - No whistles ! No whistles !
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.94,0:59:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}所有游客立刻上岸{\r}\N[ P.A. System ] Everybody, please, get out of the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.55,0:59:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}所有游客立刻上岸 让后面的上来{\r}\NDon't push. Everybody, come out of the water, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.38,1:00:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 快上岸 - 到安全的地方{\r}\NMove up past the refreshment area !
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.79,1:00:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move it, please. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.33,1:00:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Past the refreshment area.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.36,1:00:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, darlin'!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.10,1:00:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michael ! Michael !
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.41,1:01:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那里怎么回事？请回答{\r}\N[ Radio ] What's going on out there ? Give an answer, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.52,1:01:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}怎么回事？{\r}\NWhat's going on out there ?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.05,1:01:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}请回答，请回答{\r}\NCome in ! Come in !
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.99,1:01:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他叫我这么做的 他叫我这么做的{\r}\NHe made me do it. He talked me into it !
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.02,1:01:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}请各位退回来 让空气流通{\r}\NPlease, please, move back. Let's move back, please. Give these people air.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.23,1:01:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}退回来！{\r}\NPlease, move back. Move back.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.50,1:01:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}马丁，只是恶作剧{\r}\N[ Hooper ] It's just a hoax. 
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.43,1:01:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}两个小孩背着假鳍{\r}\NThere are 2 kids with a cardboard fin.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.44,1:01:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}游客都还好吧？{\r}\NIs everyone there okay ? Did everyone get out all right ?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.24,1:01:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}各位，我们开了个鲨鱼鳍的玩笑{\r}\N[ P.A. System ] Folks, we had...\Nsome practical jokers out there with a big fin.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.37,1:01:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}鲨鱼！{\r}\NShark !
Dialogue: 0,1:01:37.10,1:01:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是鲨鱼！{\r}\NThe shark !
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.60,1:01:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}它游进海湾了！ 鲨鱼游进海湾了{\r}\N[ Woman ] It's going into the pond! Shark in the estuary!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.61,1:01:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}又怎么了？{\r}\NNow what ?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.64,1:01:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}麦克在水湾里{\r}\NMichael's in the pond.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.75,1:01:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}鲨鱼在水湾里，快想个办法！{\r}\NIt's going in the pond!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:48.95,1:01:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}鲨鱼在水湾里！水湾里！{\r}\NSomebody do something! It's in the pond!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.09,1:01:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}鲨鱼在水湾里！{\r}\NIn the pond! The shark!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.93,1:02:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 快点弄好 - 什么事都弄不好{\r}\NHurry up, get that done. Can't do a damn thing--
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.27,1:02:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 把绳子解开 - 我正在解！{\r}\NGet that rope undone. Get that untangled. I'm doing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.17,1:02:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}小鬼{\r}\NHey fellas ! Fellas !
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.47,1:02:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们快点行吗？{\r}\NHaul in the sheet and make it fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.14,1:02:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[ Woman ] Shark in the pond!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.48,1:02:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你们还好吗？{\r}\NHey, you guys, you okay over there ?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:22.58,1:02:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}在水湾里{\r}\NIn the pond !
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.18,1:02:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of the water! Somebody help him !
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.62,1:03:08.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快来人拿枪！拿枪来打它！{\r}\N[ Man ] Somebody get a gun ! Get a gun and shoot it!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.33,1:03:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没人有枪吗？{\r}\NDoes anybody have a gun ?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.73,1:03:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my God ! Michael !
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.25,1:03:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 他死了吗？ - 没有，他受惊了{\r}\NIs he dead ? No, he's not. He's in shock.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.06,1:03:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[ Ellen ] Michael!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.45,1:04:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}医生说他没事了，轻微的惊吓 明早就可以回家了{\r}\NDoctor said he's okay. Mild shock. He can go home in the morning. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.63,1:04:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 我宝贝儿子还好吗？ - 我没事{\r}\NHey, how's my big kid ? I'm all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.16,1:04:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}今晚想妈？ 你可以看电视{\r}\NYou are. You gonna miss me tonight ?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.16,1:04:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 要不要我从家里带什么过来 - 我的小汽车{\r}\NYou can watch TV. Want me to bring you anything from home ? My cars. Your cars. What about ice cream ?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.80,1:04:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 要不要冰淇淋 - 咖啡{\r}\NCoffee. Coffee.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:35.21,1:04:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}想带他回家吗？{\r}\NWant to take him home ?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.15,1:04:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你是说纽约的家{\r}\NLike to New York ?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.12,1:04:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不是，这里的家{\r}\NNo, home here.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.91,1:05:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}抱歉 我很抱歉，真的{\r}\NI'm sorry. I'm truly sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:05.28,1:05:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你有笔吗？赖利 - 笔？{\r}\NGot a pen, Larry ? Pen ?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.75,1:05:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是笔没错{\r}\NYeah, pen, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.82,1:05:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你得尽力配合{\r}\N'Cause you're gonna do what you do best.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.09,1:05:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你在这支票签字 我好去请个雇员{\r}\NYou're gonna sign this voucher so I can hire a contractor.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.02,1:05:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我不知道我有权这么做{\r}\NI don't know if I can do that without--
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.03,1:05:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我要请昆特来杀鲨鱼{\r}\NI'm gonna hire Quint to kill the shark.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.70,1:05:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 八月 - 什么？{\r}\N[ Mumbling ] August. What ?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.00,1:05:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你胡说什么？夏天快过了{\r}\NWhat are you talking about ? Summer is over.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.87,1:05:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你是鲨鱼市的市长 那些人认为是你要开放浴场的{\r}\NYou're the mayor of Shark City. These people think you want the beaches open.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.47,1:05:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我是为了本镇的利益着想{\r}\NI was acting in the town's best interest.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.14,1:05:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没错！你是为本镇的利益着想 所以你得做这件事{\r}\NYou were, and that's why you're gonna do the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.85,1:05:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你得签名，照昆特的条件 付钱给他{\r}\NSign this and pay that guy what he wants. Martin.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.85,1:05:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}马丁K{\r}\NMartin.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.62,1:05:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我孩子也在海滩玩{\r}\NMy kids were on that beach too.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.10,1:06:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}签字吧，赖利{\r}\NSign it, Larry.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.01,1:06:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}一万元，每天二百 抓到与否照算{\r}\N[ Quint ] $ 1 0,000. $ 200 a day whether I catch him or not.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.92,1:06:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没问题{\r}\N[ Brody ] You've got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.25,1:06:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别让市长来烦我 我不想听他那套歪理{\r}\NGet the mayor off my back so I don't have any more of this zoning crap.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.45,1:06:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}也没问题{\r}\NYou've got that.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:22.99,1:06:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}一箱白兰地，午餐由你提供{\r}\NOne case of apricot brandy. You buy the lunch.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.99,1:06:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}二箱！回来再供应晚餐{\r}\NTwo cases. You get dinner when you get back.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.33,1:06:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}香槟，鹅干酱 伊朗鱼子酱{\r}\N[ Quint ] Champagne, pate de foie gras, Iranian caviar...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:33.73,1:06:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别忘了还要彩色电视机{\r}\Nand don't forget the color TV.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.37,1:06:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}警长，你尝口看看 我自己做的{\r}\NHey, Chief, try this. Made it myself. Pretty good stuff.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.47,1:06:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 相当不错 - 谢谢{\r}\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.91,1:06:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}敬那些用弓形腿游泳的女人{\r}\N[ Quint ] Here's to swimmin' with bowlegged women.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.09,1:06:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}失陪一下，警长{\r}\N[ Indistinct Noise ] Excuse me, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:10.87,1:07:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}六十岁以下的好手都找不到{\r}\N[ Quint ] Can't get a good man these days under 60.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.57,1:07:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 全在三十五年前就死了 - 别喝那种酒{\r}\NAll gone at least 35 years.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.91,1:07:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}昆特先生{\r}\NDon't drink that. [ Quint Mumbling ]
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.78,1:07:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}昆特先生，你需要一位帮手{\r}\NMr. Quint ? Mr. Quint ? Mr. Quint, you're gonna need an extra hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.68,1:07:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 这位是麦特胡柏 - 我知道他是谁{\r}\NThis is Matt Hooper. I know who he is.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.35,1:07:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 我在讯太平洋号上干过船员 - 太平间？{\r}\NI've crewed three trans-pacs. Transplants ?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.32,1:07:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 他是海洋研究所的人 - 也在美国实验杯号{\r}\NHe's from the oceanographic institute. An America's Cup trial.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.96,1:07:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}胡柏先生，只搭几天游艇 还差的远了{\r}\NI'm not talkin' about pleasure boatin' or day sailin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.86,1:07:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我要找以航海维生的人 这趟是去捕鲨{\r}\NI'm talkin'about workin' for a livin', sharkin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.10,1:07:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我可不是那种普通的捕鱼O{\r}\NI'm not talking about hooking some dogfish or sand shark.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:45.34,1:07:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 我的目的是要抓条大白鲨 - 口气很大{\r}\NI'm talking about finding a great white.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.57,1:07:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你的口气蛮大的{\r}\NPorkers ? Talking about porkers, Mr. Hooper ?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.85,1:07:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你打个缩短节给我看看{\r}\NTie me a sheepshank.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.55,1:08:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我已经很久没玩这套了{\r}\N[ Sighing ] I haven't had to pass basic seamanship in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.86,1:08:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你没说想要多短{\r}\NYou didn't say how short you wanted it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.96,1:08:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}还算可以吧？{\r}\NHow's that ?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.83,1:08:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}手伸出来{\r}\NGive me your hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.90,1:08:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}肉白无力？{\r}\NDogfish ?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.47,1:08:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}值五千的鱼网，抓了值二千的鱼{\r}\NYou got a $5,000 net and $2,000 worth of fish.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:23.01,1:08:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}等你拉完了网，你这双小白手{\r}\NAlong comes Mr. Whitey. By the time he's finished with that net...
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.61,1:08:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}将像剪刀剪破的白纸一样{\r}\Nit looks like a kiddie's scissors class cut it up for a paper doll.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.25,1:08:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你这双小白手只配去数钞票{\r}\NYou got city hands. You've been countin' money all your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.22,1:08:38.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我可不想听黑手阶级的狂言狂语{\r}\NAll right, all right ! I don't need this ! I don't need this working-class hero crap.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.16,1:08:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你该不会在船上这样对他吧{\r}\NYou're not gonna do this aboard the ship, are you ?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.39,1:08:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}看来我还是自个去吧{\r}\NMaybe I should go alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.73,1:08:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这件事由我来负责支派{\r}\NIt's my party. It's my charter.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.00,1:08:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你负责是没错，但是船是我的{\r}\NYeah, it's your charter. It's my vessel !
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.41,1:08:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你上了我的船{\r}\NWhen you're on board my vessel, I'm mate, master,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.38,1:09:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我就是大副，二副，驾驶 再兼船长{\r}\Npilot and I'm captain.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.81,1:09:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你要他上来船上当压舱货？{\r}\NTake him for ballast, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.55,1:09:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我答应你{\r}\NYou got him.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.53,1:09:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pliers, iron.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.53,1:09:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}鱼叉、探照灯K{\r}\N[ Hooper ] Sample bottles, dye marker, flares, safety float,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.80,1:09:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}温度计，鱼枪K{\r}\Ntemperature gauge, spear gun, SMG--
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.67,1:09:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你这算什么 半调子的太空人吗？{\r}\NWhat are ya, some kind of half-assed astronaut ?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.42,1:09:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}把这个拿到下面去绑牢{\r}\N[ Quint ] Take that stuff below and lash it secure.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.92,1:09:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}老天爷{\r}\NJesus H. Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.49,1:09:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我小的时候 每个小孩都想当鱼枪手{\r}\NWhen I was a boy, every squirt wanted to be... a harpooner or swordfisherman.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.00,1:09:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你拿这些啥玩意？ 手提式莲蓬头，还是猴子笼{\r}\NWhat you got here ? A portable shower or monkey cage ?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.40,1:09:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是防鲨笼{\r}\NAnti-shark cage.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.90,1:10:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}防鲨笼{\r}\NAnti-shark cage.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.37,1:10:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你要进笼子里？{\r}\NYou go inside the cage ?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.78,1:10:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}笼子放进海里 你也要下海{\r}\NCage goes in the water ? You go in the water ?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.15,1:10:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}鲨鱼可是也在海里 是咱们的鲨鱼{\r}\NShark's in the water ? Our shark ?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.72,1:10:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}再会吧 美丽的西班牙姑娘{\r}\N# Farewell and adieu to you fair Spanish ladies #
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.09,1:10:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}再会吧 美丽的西班牙姑娘{\r}\N# Farewell and adieu you ladies of Spain #
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.83,1:10:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我已奉命{\r}\N# For we've received orders  #
Dialogue: 0,1:10:27.67,1:10:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}搭船回波士顿{\r}\Nfor to sail back to Boston
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.14,1:10:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这一别，不知何年何月再见{\r}\NAnd so nevermore shall we see you again
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.38,1:10:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 晕船药带了吗？ - 带了{\r}\NDid you take your Dramamine ? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.55,1:10:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我在你黑袜子里多放了一副眼镜{\r}\NI put an extra pair of glasses in your black socks.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.92,1:10:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}还有一瓶鼻药水 氧化锌在急救包里{\r}\NThere's the stuff for your nose, the zinc oxide, and Blistex is in the kit.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.49,1:10:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}狗杂碎！{\r}\N[ Quint ] Son of a bitch !
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.99,1:10:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}现在的女孩真他妈的笨 什么事都做不好{\r}\NGoddamn women today can't handle nothin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.56,1:11:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}现在的小姐 就跟他们的祖母一样笨{\r}\NYoung girls ain't smart like their grandmothers.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.17,1:11:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}一定是昆特{\r}\NThat's got to be Quint. Colorful, isn't he ?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.24,1:11:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 这人真不简单 - 我有点怕他{\r}\NHe scares me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.37,1:11:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}壁炉暂时别用{\r}\NDon't use the fireplace. I haven't fixed the flue yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.61,1:11:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}要我怎么跟孩子说{\r}\NWhat am I gonna tell the kids ?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.72,1:11:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}就说我去钓鱼好了{\r}\NTell 'em I'm going fishing.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.66,1:11:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别婆婆妈妈的，警长 穷蘑菇什么！{\r}\N[ Quint ] Break it up, will ya, Chief? Daylight's wastin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.73,1:11:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}船首、船尾注意{\r}\NFront, bow. back, stern. Don't get it right, squirt,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.16,1:11:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}最好别搞错 否则老子从窗口丢你下海{\r}\NI'll throw your ass out the round window on the side!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.87,1:11:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}得了吧，警长 又不是童子军去野餐{\r}\NCome on, Chief, this isn't a picnic.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.61,1:11:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你可没忘记带救生圈{\r}\NSee ya got your rubbers. [ Laughing ]
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.88,1:11:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}里面躺着玛莉李的尸体{\r}\NHere lies the body of Mary Lee.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.25,1:11:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}死年103岁{\r}\NDied at the age of 1 03.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.51,1:11:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}连守了15年的贞操{\r}\NFor 1 5 years she kept her virginity,
Dialogue: 0,1:11:52.45,1:11:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}在这一带名声清白{\r}\Nnot a bad record for this vicinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.35,1:11:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好了，行政官 系好安全带{\r}\NAll right, Commissioner, fasten your safety belts.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.29,1:12:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}胡柏，如果你看见鲨鱼 就把它吞下去！{\r}\NIf you see a shark, Hooper, swallow.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.90,1:12:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}潜望镜上升 装备好{\r}\N[ Quint ] Up periscope. Rig for depth charge.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.60,1:12:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}准备防火训练{\r}\NStand by... fire drill.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.04,1:12:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}如何，警长？ 警长夫人还好吗？{\r}\NYou know what I'm talkin'about, Chief? How's the missus, Chief?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.15,1:12:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}如果他们不喜欢你出海 等你回航，他们可能会高兴极了{\r}\NIf they don't like you goin' out, they'll love you comin' in.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.09,1:12:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,# Oh, yo, ho, ho and a bottle of rum #
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.06,1:12:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,# Fifteen men on the dead man's chest #
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.83,1:12:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}“欧卡号”{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.31,1:12:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好好保重吧 我们还有五英里才到{\r}\NKeep that chum line goin'. We got five miles on him.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.78,1:13:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 是谁在驾驶？ - 没有谁，是浪潮{\r}\NWho's driving this boat ? Nobody, the tide.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.29,1:13:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}有一次我抓了一条 16英尺长的大鱼{\r}\NOne time I got a 1 6-footer off Montauk.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.69,1:13:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}连打了两排子弹 才制住它，总算拉上船来{\r}\NHad to stick two barrels in him to wear him down and bring him up.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.53,1:13:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}现在年轻人出海 什么都有{\r}\NNowadays these kids take out everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.06,1:13:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}雷达，声纳{\r}\NRadar, sonar,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.27,1:13:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}还有电动牙刷{\r}\Nelectric toothbrushes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.44,1:13:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}老天爷{\r}\NJesus H. Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:19.77,1:13:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}警长，最好再丢一个诱饵{\r}\NHey, Chief, best drop another chum marker.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.00,1:13:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}该死，马丁{\r}\N[ Hooper ] Damn it, Martin !
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.90,1:13:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这是压缩空气筒{\r}\NThis is compressed air.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.24,1:13:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 这算是什么绳结？ - 你拉错了绳结{\r}\NWhat the hell kind of a knot was that ? You pulled the wrong one !
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.47,1:13:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}如果稍有差错，可能会爆炸{\r}\NYou screw around with these tanks and they're gonna blow up.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.98,1:14:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你带来的这些行头 都是贵重的好东西{\r}\NYeah, real fine, expensive gear you brought out here.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:02.15,1:14:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}就是不知道混蛋鲨鱼 看了会怎样{\r}\NBut I don't know what that shark's gonna do with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.65,1:14:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}也许会一口吃掉吧 有一次我看到鲨鱼吞下安乐椅{\r}\NMight eat it, I suppose. Seen one eat a rockin' chair.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.92,1:14:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}警长{\r}\NHey, Chiefy, next time,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.69,1:14:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}下次你最好先问我 该拉哪条绳子{\r}\Njust ask me which line to pull, right ?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.70,1:14:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}棕色小鳗鱼钻出动{\r}\N[ Quint ] Little brown eel comes out of the cave,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.37,1:14:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}游进洞口{\r}\Nswims into the hole,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.61,1:14:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}再出洞口 再进洞口{\r}\Ncomes out of the hole, goes back to the cave again.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.84,1:14:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}并不太容易吧，警长{\r}\NNot too good, is it, Chief?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.85,1:14:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}天下无易事，再一次{\r}\NWell, nothing's easy, is it ? One more time.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.88,1:15:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[ Brody ] The brown eel comes out of the cave.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:57.93,1:15:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我会了！{\r}\NHey ! I got it !
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.20,1:16:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 什么？ - 到我后面来{\r}\NWhat ? Get behind me !
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.77,1:16:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}胡柏，退后！{\r}\N[ Quint ] Hooper, reverse her!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.41,1:16:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}绳子跑了不少{\r}\NTakin' a hell of a lot of line !
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.51,1:16:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}警长，把勺子拿来 用水浇轮轴！{\r}\NChief, get the scoop. Wet the reel !
Dialogue: 0,1:16:19.55,1:16:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}胡柏，退后！{\r}\NHooper, reverse her !
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.69,1:16:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}头低下来，警长！ 船开始摇了！到我后面{\r}\NDuck your head down. We're swinging. Get behind me again.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.36,1:16:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}水不要了！ 你想淹死我！{\r}\NNo more water. Don't drown me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.76,1:16:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}胡柏，你这白痴 右舷！你没在看吗？{\r}\NHooper, you idiot ! Starboard ! Ain't you watchin' it ?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:40.11,1:16:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}胡柏，空档！{\r}\N[ Quint ] Hooper, neutral.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.78,1:16:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这会又跑哪里去了{\r}\NWhere's he goin' now ?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:51.25,1:16:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别想骗我{\r}\NHe ain't foolin' me.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.12,1:16:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这下又躲到哪去？{\r}\NWhat's he yankin' on now ?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.19,1:16:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}出来试试看{\r}\NGo on. Try it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.30,1:17:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}很难说，警长 若不是很聪明，就是很笨{\r}\NI don't know, Chief. He's very smart or very dumb.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.15,1:17:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus Chr--
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.22,1:17:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}它沉到船下面 它沉到船下面{\r}\NHe's gone under. Gone under the boat.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.79,1:17:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}它沉到船下面{\r}\NI think he's gone under the boat.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.56,1:17:34.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不会这么简单{\r}\NYeah, it's too easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.23,1:17:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}它是条狡猾的大鱼 跑到船下面去了{\r}\NHe ain't a smart, big fish. He's gone under the boat.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.10,1:17:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}船稳住！ 我要抓大鱼了{\r}\NKeep it steady now. I got somethin' very big.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.70,1:17:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我看不见得{\r}\NI don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.20,1:17:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}警长，手套戴上{\r}\NChief, Chief, put your gloves on.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.54,1:17:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你俩都戴上手套{\r}\NPut your gloves on, both of ya.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.11,1:17:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}它又准备出来了{\r}\NGettin'ready to run out again.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.81,1:17:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}昆特，放了它{\r}\NQuint, let it go.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.61,1:18:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你在实验室也许支使得了别人 但在我船上你只是压舱货{\r}\NYou may be a big yahoo in the lab, but here you're just supercargo.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.42,1:18:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}如果你不想游泳回家 就快给我下来{\r}\NIf you don't want to backstroke home, get down here.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.75,1:18:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好吧，听不听随便你{\r}\NAll right, you don't want to listen to me, don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.22,1:18:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那不是鲨鱼！{\r}\NIt's not a shark.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.76,1:18:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 铁丝露出来了！ - 帮我解开{\r}\NThe wire's showing. The wire's showing ! Unbuckle me.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.46,1:18:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 到另一边去 - 若不是鱿鱼就是剑鱼{\r}\NGet the other side. It's tuna or swordfish.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.67,1:18:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}浪费我们时间{\r}\NWastin' our time.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.77,1:18:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}拉住杆子 胡柏！帮警长一下{\r}\NOkay, take this rod. Give the chief a hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.44,1:18:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 好 - 狗屎{\r}\NRight ! Oh, shit !
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.99,1:18:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是马林鱼也可能是黄貂鱼{\r}\NIt may be a marlin or a stingray,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.76,1:18:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但绝对是条大的{\r}\Nbut it's definitely a game fish. Ohh--
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.90,1:18:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}大鱼？{\r}\NGamin' fish, eh ? Marlin, stingray ?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.91,1:18:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}马林鱼？黄貂鱼？ 自作聪明的东西{\r}\NBit through this piano wire ? Don't tell me my business.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.24,1:18:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}以后少在我面前卖弄 你给我上舰桥上去{\r}\NGet back on the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.08,1:19:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}昆特，这不能证明什么{\r}\NDoesn't prove a thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.98,1:19:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}胡柏先生 不过有件事可以证明{\r}\NIt proves one thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:05.35,1:19:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这证明你们这些有钱的大学生{\r}\NIt proves you wealthy college boys don't have the education...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.35,1:19:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}却没有勇气承认自己的错误{\r}\Nto admit when you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.93,1:19:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这有何意义？ 不是钩就是绳子{\r}\NWhat's the point ? Hooks and lines ?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.14,1:19:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没了再挂一个就是了{\r}\NWell, you lose one, you rig one.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.97,1:19:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}朝东南方全速前进{\r}\N[ Engine Starting ] Hooper ! Twelve minutes, south southeast, full throttle.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.55,1:19:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}遵命，船长！{\r}\NAye, aye, sir. [ Grumbling ]
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.15,1:19:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我的做法你看出来了吧 先把它诱出水面{\r}\NSee what I do, Chief, is trick 'em to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.85,1:19:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}然后再射它{\r}\NI jab at 'em. I'm not gonna haul 'em up like catfish.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.89,1:19:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我不打算像捉鲶鱼一样 用网子拖{\r}\NHooper !
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.46,1:19:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}全速前进！{\r}\NFull throttle!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.59,1:19:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这种窝囊气我快受不了了{\r}\NI don't have to take this abuse much longer.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:52.10,1:19:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你的头在流血了 急救箱在那里{\r}\NYour head's bleedin'. First aid there.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.03,1:20:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}布洛迪，你再放饵{\r}\NBrody, start that chum line again, will ya ?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.87,1:20:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}让胡柏接手{\r}\NLet Hooper take a turn.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.87,1:20:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}胡柏在开船，警长{\r}\NHooper drives the boat.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.55,1:20:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别在自摸了，胡柏 请你慢速前进{\r}\NStop playin' with yourself. Slow ahead, if you please.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.29,1:20:55.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你听到了没有，慢速前进{\r}\NYa heard him. Slow ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.30,1:21:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}慢速前进，我也会慢速前进{\r}\NSlow ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.94,1:21:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}为何不下来，丢这些臭鱼饵{\r}\NI can go slow ahead. Come on down and chum some of this shit.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.36,1:21:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你得换条大船才保得住{\r}\NYou're gonna need a bigger boat.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.81,1:21:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}引擎熄掉{\r}\NShut off that engine !
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.34,1:22:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}有二十英尺长{\r}\N- That's a twenty-footer. - Twenty-five.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.01,1:22:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}二十五英尺，至少三吨重{\r}\NThree tons of him.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.18,1:22:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们得换大船对吗？{\r}\NWe're gonna need a bigger boat, right ?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.95,1:22:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快点下手吧{\r}\NGotta get to work. How do we handle this ?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.59,1:22:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}怎么对付得了，怎么对付呀{\r}\N[ Hooper ] Come front. I need you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.06,1:22:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}它在绕船打转！看看它多大{\r}\N[ Hooper ] He's circling the boat.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.13,1:22:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Martin.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.17,1:22:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}艾米提灯塔，呼叫欧卡{\r}\N[ Radio ] Amity light station to Orca. This is Amity light station to Orca. Come in, Orca.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.08,1:22:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 快回答 - 欧卡请说{\r}\NOrca. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.65,1:23:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 布洛迪太太有话要说 - 接过来{\r}\NI have Mrs. Martin Brody here. Put her on.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.75,1:23:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 马丁，快去！ - 我才不过去！{\r}\N[ Hooper ] Go on, Martin, move, move! I'm not going out there!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.92,1:23:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}到桶子旁边，到桶子旁边{\r}\NBeyond the barrels, go to the end of the barrels.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.36,1:23:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 再过去 - 什么？{\r}\NFurther out ! What ?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.86,1:23:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 再过去！ - 为什么？{\r}\NGo further out ! What for ?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.36,1:23:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 再过去 - 为什么？{\r}\NGo further out ! What for ?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.40,1:23:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}请你到甲板旁边行吗{\r}\NWill you go to the end of the pulpit, please ? What ?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.40,1:23:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 为什么？ - 我拍照时需要你在前面陪衬{\r}\NWhat for ? I need something in the foreground to give it scale.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.84,1:23:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}陪衬个屁！{\r}\NForeground, my ass !
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.34,1:23:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你先生正在钓鱼 刚钓到几条纹鱼{\r}\NYour husband's all right. He's fishing. Just caught a couple of stripers.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.48,1:23:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们带回去当晚餐 目前还没有什么发现，完毕{\r}\NWe're bringin' dinner. We haven't seen anything. Over. Out.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:29.55,1:23:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 我不要留在那里！ - 我求求你！{\r}\NI'm not staying here. I'm begging you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.95,1:23:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}该死！ 来呀，甜心{\r}\NMartin, goddamn it ! Come here, darlin', come here !
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.52,1:23:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}太美了！{\r}\N[ Hooper ] Beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.69,1:23:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}警长，我要你到舰桥上 朝前方进行{\r}\NChief, get on the bridge. Take her forward, steady.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.46,1:23:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 我一辈子也没开过船 - 稳着开就好{\r}\NI've never steered a boat in my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.20,1:23:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}胡柏先生{\r}\NWatch my hand. Take her steady.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.17,1:23:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}把线绑在第一个桶子上{\r}\NMr. Hooper, attach the end of this line to the first keg.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.20,1:23:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我非先在它头上开一枪不可{\r}\NI've got to get a good shot at that porker's head.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.29,1:24:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}它来了{\r}\NComin', 
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.72,1:24:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}来了{\r}\Ncomin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.43,1:24:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}待在甲板{\r}\NHooper, get clear of the barrel.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.00,1:24:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}胡柏{\r}\NHooper !
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.43,1:24:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 绑好 - 昆特，轮到你受罪了{\r}\NTie it up, will ya ? Your turn, Quint.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.47,1:24:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}胡柏，你在哪？{\r}\NHooper, where are ya ?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.47,1:24:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快点行吗？绑好{\r}\NHooper, hurry it up now. Tie it on.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.38,1:24:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 别搞砸了 - 别等我{\r}\NHurry up, he's comin' straight for us. Don't screw it up. Don't wait for me !
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.15,1:24:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快，胡柏！{\r}\NCome on, Hooper,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.99,1:24:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快绑！{\r}\NHurry up ! Tie it on !
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.59,1:24:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now. Now.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.39,1:24:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}开枪！昆特，杀了它！{\r}\N[ Brody ] Kill him, Quint. Kill him !
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.73,1:24:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}现在！{\r}\NNow !
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.80,1:24:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}开枪！{\r}\N- Shoot ! - [ Gunshot ]
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.30,1:24:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}时间刚好！{\r}\NTime !
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.80,1:25:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[ Quint ] What were you doin' ? I didn't get a clean shot in the head.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.37,1:25:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你在干嘛？ 我没瞄准它的头部{\r}\N[ Quint ] What were you doin' ? I didn't get a clean shot in the head.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.98,1:25:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好吧，看看桶子什么时候浮起来{\r}\NAll right, let's see how long that barrel takes to bring him up.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.45,1:25:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}再放一个桶子，我要跟上了！{\r}\NFree another barrel. I'm coming around again.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.07,1:26:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 我们现在放弃了是吗？ - 它带走了一个桶子{\r}\NWhat do we do now ? We're quitting, right ?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.11,1:26:13.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们要待在这里，等它出来{\r}\N[ Quint ] We've got one barrel on him. We stay until we find him again.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.81,1:26:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}可是我们为何不呼叫他们 派条大船来{\r}\NWe could radio in and get a bigger boat--
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.57,1:26:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}警长{\r}\NChief.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.91,1:26:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别担心{\r}\NDon't you worry about it, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.57,1:26:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不会留疤的{\r}\NIt won't be permanent.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.58,1:26:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}要看永久的伤口吗？{\r}\NWant to see something permanent, boom, boom, boom ?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.72,1:26:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}胡柏{\r}\NHey, Hoop, 
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.22,1:26:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你想感觉一下永久？{\r}\Nyou wanna feel something permanent ?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.26,1:27:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}把你的手放在我的帽子下 有一块肿起来的地方{\r}\NJust put your hand underneath my cap. Feel that little lump ?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.36,1:27:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}诺可诺兰斯 波士顿，圣彼得日{\r}\NKnocko Nolans, St. Paddy's Day, Boston.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.84,1:27:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我被咬到过{\r}\NI got that beat.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.24,1:27:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我被咬到过{\r}\NI got that beat.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.34,1:27:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}有条海鳗{\r}\NThat's a moray eel.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.61,1:27:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}咬穿我的潜水装{\r}\NBit right through my wet suit.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.08,1:27:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}胡柏，听着{\r}\NHoop, now, listen, I don't know about that,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.15,1:27:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我不知道 但我参加摔角比赛{\r}\Nbut I entered an arm wrestling contest...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.35,1:27:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}在旧金山的奥可酒吧{\r}\Nin an Okie bar in San Francisco.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.76,1:27:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我不能伸直 知道为什么吗？{\r}\NI can't extend that, you know why ?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:35.26,1:27:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我参加准决赛 庆祝我第三个老婆过世{\r}\NI was in the semifinal, celebratin' my wife's demise.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.76,1:27:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}中国佬大汉 拉我过去{\r}\NBig Chinese fella pulled me right over.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:55.28,1:27:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}看{\r}\NLook at that.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.25,1:28:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}公牛白眼鲛{\r}\NIt was a bull shark.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.55,1:28:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}它抓我 当我拿样品的时候{\r}\NHe scraped me when I was takin' samples.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.79,1:28:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}给你看样东西 长尾鲛{\r}\NI got somethin' for ya. There's a thresher. See that, Chief?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.09,1:28:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}长尾鲛的尾巴{\r}\NThresher's tail.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.93,1:28:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 长尾鲛？ - 一种鲨鱼{\r}\NThresher ?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.50,1:28:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shark.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.93,1:28:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}敬你{\r}\NYou want a drink ? Drink to your leg ?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.93,1:28:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 我敬你 - 敬我们{\r}\NI'll drink to your leg. Okay, we drink to our legs.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.34,1:28:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我这有最炫的{\r}\N[ Hooper ] I got the creme de la creme.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.34,1:28:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这里，等等{\r}\NRight here.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.88,1:28:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你看见了吗？{\r}\NSee that ?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.85,1:28:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你穿毛衣{\r}\N[ Brody ] You're wearin' a sweater.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.52,1:28:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这里 玛莉艾琳莫夫特{\r}\NRight there. Mary Ellen Moffit.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:38.06,1:28:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}她伤了我的心{\r}\NShe broke my heart. [ Laughing ]
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.07,1:28:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 那是什么？ - 什么？{\r}\NWhat's that one ? [ Quint ] What ?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.87,1:28:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那个，在你手臂上{\r}\NThat one there on your arm.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.67,1:28:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是刺青，我清除了{\r}\NOh, a tattoo. I got that removed.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.74,1:29:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别告诉我 上面写“妈”{\r}\NDon't tell me. Don't tell me. Mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.69,1:29:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}到底是什么？{\r}\NWhat is it ?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.73,1:29:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}胡柏先生 这是美军印第安纳波里号{\r}\NHooper, that's the USS Indianapolis.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.47,1:29:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你上过印第安纳波里号？{\r}\N- You were on the Indianapolis ?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:27.54,1:29:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}发生了什么事？{\r}\N- What happened ?
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.84,1:29:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}日本潜水艇在船身打了 两枚鱼雷{\r}\NJapanese submarine slammed two torpedoes into her side.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:36.31,1:29:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们从提尼安雷岛 送原子弹回来{\r}\NWas comin' back from the island of Tinian Leyte.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:40.32,1:29:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}炸广岛的那颗{\r}\NJust delivered the bomb, the Hiroshima bomb.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:46.52,1:29:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}一千一百个人掉入海中{\r}\NEleven hundred men went into the water.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.26,1:29:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}十二分钟后船也沉了{\r}\NVessel went down in 1 2 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.70,1:29:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}半小时之内还没事{\r}\NDidn't see the first shark for about half an hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.80,1:30:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}后来就是一条十三英尺的虎鲨 你可知道在海中的感受？{\r}\NTiger, 1 3-footer. Know how you know that when you're in the water ?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:01.54,1:30:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}只要看它一眼马上就知道{\r}\NYou tell by lookin' from the dorsal to the tail.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.68,1:30:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但是我们不知道{\r}\NWhat we didn't know 
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.85,1:30:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}因为这趟任务是个大秘密{\r}\Nwas our bomb mission had been so secret...
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.65,1:30:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没有人发求救信号{\r}\Nno distress signal had been sent.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.93,1:30:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}一星期后都没人知道 我们逾期未归{\r}\NThey didn't even list us as overdue for a week.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.33,1:30:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}第一眼就看到鲨鱼 游了过来{\r}\NVery first light, Chief, sharks come cruisin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:30.30,1:30:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}大伙挤成一团{\r}\NWe formed ourselves into tight groups.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:34.27,1:30:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}就像日历上滑铁炉 那场战争中的方块阵{\r}\NKinda like old squares in a battle, like you see on a calendar, like the Battle of Waterloo.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.08,1:30:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}当时的想法 万一鲨鱼过来{\r}\NThe idea was, shark comes to the nearest man,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.08,1:30:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}前面的人就大叫大喊{\r}\Nthat man starts poundin', hollerin', screamin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.95,1:30:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}或许会吓走鲨鱼{\r}\NSometimes the shark go away,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.59,1:30:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}也许根本不会走{\r}\Nsometimes he wouldn't go away.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.89,1:30:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}有时候它直瞪着你不放{\r}\NSometimes that shark looks right into ya,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:54.73,1:30:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}看着你的眼睛{\r}\Nright into your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.46,1:31:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}鲨鱼最特别的一点 它有一双痴呆的双眼{\r}\NYou know, a thing about a shark, he's got lifeless eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:02.33,1:31:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}黑色的，像娃娃的眼睛{\r}\NBlack eyes, like a doll's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:06.17,1:31:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}它游过来的时候像是死鱼{\r}\NWhen he comes at ya, doesn't seem to be livin',
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.97,1:31:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但是当它咬中你时{\r}\Nuntil he bites ya and those black eyes roll over wide.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.71,1:31:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}黑眼翻成白色{\r}\NAnd then--
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.58,1:31:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}然后就是高八度的叫声{\r}\Nthen you hear that terrible high-pitched screamin'.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:20.38,1:31:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}海水染成红色{\r}\NThe ocean turns red.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:22.75,1:31:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}混杂着拍水声，呼救声{\r}\NIn spite of the pounding and hollering, they all come in.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:28.29,1:31:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}人就这样被咬成碎片{\r}\NThey rip you to pieces.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.87,1:31:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}天亮之前{\r}\NYou know, by the end of that first dawn,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.04,1:31:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}少了一百人{\r}\Nlost a hundred men.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.24,1:31:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我也不知道有多少只鲨鱼 也许一千只{\r}\NI don't know how many sharks, maybe a thousand.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.61,1:31:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}平均一小时吃掉六个{\r}\NI don't know how many men. They averaged six an hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.08,1:31:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}星期四早上{\r}\NOn Thursday morning,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.01,1:31:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我发现一位朋友 他叫罗宾森，克利夫兰人{\r}\NI bumped into a friend of mine, Robinson, from Cleveland,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:54.99,1:31:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}棒球手{\r}\Nbaseball player, boatswain's mate.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.82,1:32:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我以为他睡着了{\r}\NI thought he was asleep.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.46,1:32:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}游过去叫醒他{\r}\NReached over to wake him up.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:05.53,1:32:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他只是上半段漂在水上{\r}\NBobbed up and down in the water like a top.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.00,1:32:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}下半部全没了{\r}\NUpended.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:13.40,1:32:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}从腰以下狠狠地被咬断{\r}\NWell, he'd been bitten in half below the waist.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.31,1:32:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}第五天中午{\r}\NNoon the fifth day, Mr. Hooper,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.71,1:32:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}一位叫洛克希德的人 开直升机看到我们{\r}\Na Lockheed Ventura saw us. He swung in low and saw us.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:27.48,1:32:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他是位年轻的驾驶员 比胡柏先生还年轻{\r}\NYoung pilot, a lot younger than Mr. Hooper.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:30.35,1:32:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}他看见我们，三小时之后{\r}\NHe saw us and come in low. Three hours later,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.32,1:32:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}叫来一架大型直升机接我们{\r}\Na big fat PBY comes down and starts to pick us up.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.93,1:32:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}那是我一生中最害怕的时刻{\r}\NThat was the time I was most frightened,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:40.50,1:32:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}等着轮到我自己{\r}\Nwaitin' for my turn.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.70,1:32:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我再也不敢穿上救生衣{\r}\NI'll never put on a life jacket again.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.31,1:32:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}当初落海的是一千一百人{\r}\NEleven hundred men went into the water.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.34,1:32:53.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}救回来的只有316人{\r}\N31 6 men come out. The sharks took the rest.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.34,1:32:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}其他人全被鲨鱼吃掉了 1945年6月29日{\r}\NJune 29, 1 945.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:00.28,1:33:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}反正{\r}\NAnyway,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.65,1:33:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}谁叫我们送原子弹{\r}\Nwe delivered the bomb.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:16.37,1:33:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}什么声音？{\r}\NWhat's that ?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.57,1:33:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}鲸鱼声{\r}\NIt's a whale.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.57,1:33:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}再见吧{\r}\N# Farewell and adieu #
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.94,1:33:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}美丽的西班牙女O{\r}\N# To you fair Spanish ladies #
Dialogue: 0,1:33:28.08,1:33:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}再见吧{\r}\N# Farewell #
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.41,1:33:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}美丽的西班牙女O{\r}\Nand adieu you ladies of Spain 
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.35,1:33:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}请引我走上回家的路{\r}\N# Show me the way to go home #
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.86,1:33:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我已疲倦渴望着休息{\r}\N# I'm tired and I wanna go to bed #
Dialogue: 0,1:33:48.40,1:33:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}一小时前{\r}\N# I had a little drink  #
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.00,1:33:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}喝的酒{\r}\Nabout an hour ago
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.54,1:33:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}如今已在我脑海中发酵{\r}\N# And it's gone right to my head #
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.68,1:34:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不论我流浪到{\r}\N# Wherever I may roam #
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.68,1:34:07.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}海角天涯{\r}\N# By land or sea or foam #
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.92,1:34:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will always hear me singin'this song [ Beeping ]
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.76,1:34:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me the way to go home
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.29,1:34:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}请引我走上回家的路{\r}\N# Boom, boom, boom Show me the way to go home #
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.33,1:34:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我已疲倦渴望着休息{\r}\N# Boom, boom I'm tired and I wanna go to bed #
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.44,1:34:30.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}一小时前饮的酒 如今已在我脑海中发酵{\r}\N# I had a little drink about an hour ago # # And it went right to my head #
Dialogue: 0,1:34:30.97,1:34:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不管我流浪到{\r}\NWherever I may roam [ Banging ]
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.98,1:34:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}海角天涯{\r}\N# On land or sea or foam #
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.08,1:34:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你将永远听我唱同一首歌{\r}\N# You can always hear me singing-- # [ Indistinct Noise ]
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.25,1:34:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}发动引擎{\r}\NStart the engines.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.66,1:34:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}开动！发动！{\r}\N[ Quint ] Fire her up ! Start the mill.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.83,1:34:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}枪弄好！{\r}\N[ Hooper ] Busting shaft.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:03.27,1:35:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}把火熄掉好吗？{\r}\NChief, put out the fire, will ya ?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.32,1:35:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 水抽掉 - 抽好了{\r}\NPump her out. Done.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.66,1:35:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 统统上甲板 - 它连灯也吃{\r}\N[ Quint ] Everybody on deck. [ Hooper ] He ate the light.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.07,1:35:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 这可真好 - 对不起{\r}\N[ Brody ] Terrific. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.37,1:35:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}昆特，你在干嘛？ 别浪费时间{\r}\N[ Hooper ] Quint, what are you doing ? Don't waste your time.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:37.14,1:35:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这有什么不对？ 老天！{\r}\N[ Quint ] What's wrong with this shark ?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.04,1:35:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}胡柏，去掌舵{\r}\N[ Quint ] Hooper, take the wheel.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.65,1:35:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}布洛迪你跟着看好它{\r}\NBrody, forward deck. Watch for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.60,1:36:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你还好吧？{\r}\NYou okay ?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.30,1:36:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}马丁，你没事吧？{\r}\NHey, Martin, you okay ?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:31.46,1:36:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}警长，左舷 左手向下拉{\r}\N[ Quint ] Hey, Chief, more left rudder. Pull your left hand down.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.47,1:36:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}拉不动！只能动三寸{\r}\NI can't. It'll only go about three inches.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:39.17,1:36:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}给水器中{\r}\N[ Hooper ] Our injectors got scored from
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.87,1:36:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}都漂满了油{\r}\Nthe salt water in the fuel.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.04,1:36:47.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}整条船都快裂了，听听就知道{\r}\N[ Quint ] The housing's bent. You can hear it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:47.31,1:36:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}再试试左舷好吗？{\r}\NTry the left rudder again, will ya ?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.45,1:36:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}再左！好，再一次{\r}\NMore left, good. Once again, now.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:53.48,1:36:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}昆特！昆特！昆特 它来了{\r}\NQuint, Quint, Quint ! There it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.85,1:36:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你说什么，警长？{\r}\NWhat do you say, Chief?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.19,1:37:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}木桶浮上来了！在船尾{\r}\NThe barrel is up. It's right in the stern.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.06,1:37:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}看来桶就在下面 拿长勾过来{\r}\NThink he's right under the keg. Grab the boat hook.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.88,1:37:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}昆特，如果无法再接近{\r}\NQuint, if we can get close enough,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.01,1:37:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我有样东西可以杀死它{\r}\NI've got things on board that'll kill him.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:26.45,1:37:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我只是要逗它出来{\r}\NJust want to goose him up. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:36.53,1:37:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.30,1:37:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}它一跑你就丢绳子 否则手就别要了{\r}\NWhen he runs, drop that rope or you'll lose your hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:46.17,1:37:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我见过手指连根都断掉{\r}\NI seen fingers torn out at the knuckles.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.01,1:37:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}全海面都是指骨 老弟，先给我一下{\r}\NWhole sea's full of'em. Give it to me a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:08.19,1:38:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}绳子拉住，别让它耍了{\r}\N[ Quint ] Haul in that line or it will foul us.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.19,1:38:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}发动引擎{\r}\NStart the engines.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.56,1:38:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你要去哪？ - 去打个电话{\r}\N- Where you goin' ? - I'm gonna make a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.67,1:38:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}哈？哈？{\r}\NHello ? Hello ?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:24.94,1:38:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}欧卡号 求救，海岸巡逻队{\r}\NHello, Mayday ! Orca. Coast Guard ?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:28.41,1:38:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}海岸巡逻队，这是欧卡号 你听见了吗？{\r}\N[ Brody ] Coast Guard, this is Orca. Do you read me ?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.25,1:38:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这是欧卡号{\r}\NCoast Guard, this is Orca, do you--
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.79,1:38:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}抱歉了，警长{\r}\NExcuse me, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.69,1:38:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好极了！这下好极了！{\r}\NThat's great ! That's just great !
Dialogue: 0,1:38:44.96,1:38:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}这下子咱们怎么办？{\r}\NNow where the hell are we, huh ?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.30,1:38:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你别想狡赖，你知道吗？{\r}\NYou're certifiable, Quint, do you know that ?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.03,1:38:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 是，是K - 你别想狡赖！{\r}\NYou're certifiable ! Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:53.57,1:38:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我告诉你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.17,1:38:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}各位{\r}\N[ Hooper ] Boys. Oh, boys.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.14,1:38:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我看它要回来吃午餐了{\r}\NI think he's come back for his noon feeding.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.21,1:39:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}再帮我钩个桶子{\r}\NHook me up another barrel !
Dialogue: 0,1:39:32.21,1:39:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们去追它{\r}\NTake her around after him !
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.59,1:39:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}全速前进！与它并行！{\r}\N[ Quint ] Full throttle! Get me right up alongside him.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.90,1:39:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我开不了这么快 船会吃不消！{\r}\N[ Hooper ] I can't! It's not gonna take it!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:15.02,1:40:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}左舷五度！{\r}\NFive degrees port.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:24.73,1:40:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好！方向不变！{\r}\NAll right, hold your course.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.90,1:40:34.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}再左五度{\r}\NFive degrees port now.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:38.41,1:40:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}方向不变{\r}\NHold your course.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:41.08,1:40:43.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 好快的鱼 - 看我的手势！{\r}\NFast fish. [ Quint ] Watch my hand.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.75,1:40:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}看着我的手，跟我来{\r}\NBe sure you watch my hand now. Follow me. Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.42,1:40:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}看着它！右舷！{\r}\NAll right, watch now. Starboard, starboard!
Dialogue: 0,1:40:53.72,1:40:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}压下去！胡柏{\r}\NRun him down, Hooper.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.26,1:40:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}压下去！{\r}\NRun him down ! Run him down !
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.70,1:41:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}原地转{\r}\NHard aport !
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.80,1:41:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}看好它！右舷！右舷！{\r}\N[ Quint ] Watch him ! Starboard! Starboard!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:33.03,1:41:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}真不敢相信，两个木桶 它还沉得下去！{\r}\N[ Brody ] I can't believe it! Two barrels and he's going down again.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.87,1:41:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}真不可思议{\r}\NHe's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.85,1:41:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 又浮上来了 - 又有什么花招？{\r}\NThey're up again ! Now what ?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.13,1:42:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们为何不把鲨鱼引到岸上{\r}\NWhy don't we lead the shark to shore instead
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.33,1:42:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}总比让它引到外海好{\r}\Nof him leading us to sea ?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.63,1:42:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}拿两根杆子来{\r}\NGrab a couple of poles, okay ?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:14.67,1:42:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}抓稳！要转了{\r}\NHang on now, we're goin' around.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:16.97,1:42:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}换成右舷，慢慢来{\r}\N[ Quint ] Into starboard, easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.01,1:42:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}再回原方向，你看着木桶{\r}\NI'm gonna back her up now. Watch those barrels, boys. Watch them !
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.49,1:42:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好了，各位，钩回来{\r}\NAll right, gentlemen, snag 'em.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:37.63,1:42:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}现在绑在船首钩上{\r}\NNow then, tie them to the stern cleats.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.67,1:42:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}布洛迪，绳头绑在钩上{\r}\NBrody, bring your end around the cleat!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.44,1:42:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对，打个死结{\r}\NThat's right. It'll lock itself off.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.04,1:42:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}布洛迪，别拉到他{\r}\NGive him room, Brody!
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.14,1:42:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别太靠近绳子{\r}\NAaah ! Stay clear of the line!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.32,1:43:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}小心，别靠近{\r}\NWatch it. Stand clear.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.16,1:43:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别靠近挂钩！{\r}\NStand away from those stern cleats !
Dialogue: 0,1:43:28.71,1:43:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}镇上有个计程车司机{\r}\NBack home we got a taxidermy man.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.08,1:43:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}等我把鲨鱼捉回去 他一定心脏病发{\r}\NHe gonna have a heart attack when he see what I brung.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:41.06,1:43:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快退回来！钩子松了！{\r}\NThrottle back ! You're losing your cleats !
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.49,1:43:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}瞧瞧 老天，两个都松了{\r}\N[ Hooper ] Look at that mother. This one too. They're both going.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.37,1:43:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}它一直跟着绳子往上吃{\r}\NHe's eating his way right through that line.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.77,1:43:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}对，它冲着我们来{\r}\NYeah, he's working his way right up to us. Quint !
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.10,1:43:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}昆特，快！{\r}\N[ Hooper ] Come on, Quint!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:56.81,1:43:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}昆特！{\r}\NHurry! Quint!
Dialogue: 0,1:43:58.84,1:44:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别挡路{\r}\NOut of my way.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.28,1:44:06.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}小心！{\r}\N[ Quint ] Watch it!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:10.42,1:44:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}解开！钩子要拔掉了{\r}\NUntie us ! He'll pull out the transom !
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.56,1:44:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快点！ 我们用另一条线牵着它！{\r}\N[ Quint ] Make it fast! We'll get another line in him.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:18.90,1:44:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没办法！它想逃！{\r}\NI can't ! He's trying to run !
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.00,1:44:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,[ Quint ] He's gonna give us a ride!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.07,1:44:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快拉呀，狗杂碎！{\r}\N[ Quint ] Pull, you son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.64,1:44:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}希望你的背断掉{\r}\NHope your back breaks ! Go on !
Dialogue: 0,1:44:28.71,1:44:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}拉！使劲拉！{\r}\NPull your bloody heart out !
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.24,1:44:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}解开！{\r}\NTie him off ! Do it. Tie him off !
Dialogue: 0,1:44:37.61,1:44:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不可能！{\r}\NIt's impossible ! It's impossible !
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.52,1:44:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}绳子太紧了！它在拉我们！{\r}\NThe line is too tight. He's towing us !
Dialogue: 0,1:44:44.52,1:44:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们要松开 不然它会把钩子拉掉{\r}\NCut him loose or he'll pull the transom off !
Dialogue: 0,1:44:47.42,1:44:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}船要毁了！切断！快！{\r}\N[ Hooper ] We're breaking up ! Cut it, man. It's coming off !
Dialogue: 0,1:44:50.86,1:44:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 拿东西来切断！ - 拿斧头来！{\r}\N[ Hooper ] The ax! Get the ax!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:54.73,1:44:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快撑不住了！{\r}\NWe're breaking up ! We're breaking up !
Dialogue: 0,1:44:57.93,1:45:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 切！ - 小心你的手！{\r}\NCut it ! Cut it ! Watch your hands!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.57,1:45:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 抓紧！ - 切，昆特！我抓不住！{\r}\NCome on ! Hold it ! [ Hooper ] Cut it! I can't hold it!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.74,1:45:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it! Cut it!
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.76,1:45:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}三个桶子它沉不下去{\r}\NCan't stay down with three barrels on him.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.26,1:45:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}三个，它别做梦了{\r}\NNot with three barrels, he can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.80,1:45:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们怎么办？{\r}\NWhat about us ? Hooper,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.80,1:45:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}把你前面的啷桶拿来{\r}\Nget the pump out of the locker, will you ?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:35.71,1:45:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们要下水{\r}\NWe're gonna sink, aren't we ?
Dialogue: 0,1:45:36.97,1:45:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}胡柏，看着桶子{\r}\NHooper, keep an eye on the barrels.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.18,1:45:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}快点抽，警长{\r}\NPump it out, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.22,1:45:48.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}是不是要下沉{\r}\NTrying to go under !
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.95,1:45:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不可能！三个桶它没办法{\r}\NHe can't with three barrels on him.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:27.22,1:46:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}你以前碰过这么大的吗？{\r}\NYou ever have one do this before ?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:31.63,1:46:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}没有{\r}\NHell, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:44.34,1:46:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}抓稳了！{\r}\N[ Banging ] [ Quint ] Hold fast!
Dialogue: 0,1:47:04.23,1:47:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}它追我们！真不敢相信{\r}\N[ Hooper ] He's chasing us. I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:11.87,1:47:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我要拉它到浅水去{\r}\NI'm gonna draw him into the shallows.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:14.44,1:47:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我要拉它去浅滩！让它死{\r}\NDraw him into shallow water, draw him in and drown him.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:19.08,1:47:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 我们前进，布洛迪 - 谢谢上帝{\r}\NWe're headin' in, Brody. Thank Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.25,1:47:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 你以前见过这么大的白鲨吗 - 没有{\r}\NHave you ever had a great white do this ? No !
Dialogue: 0,1:47:37.99,1:47:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我们还要走多远？{\r}\NHow far do we have to go ?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:42.70,1:47:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}别让船吃不消{\r}\NQuint, don't put that much pressure on them.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:55.25,1:47:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 该死！ - 闭嘴！给我回去看着！{\r}\NQuint, goddamn it ! Shut up ! Get back there !
Dialogue: 0,1:47:58.62,1:48:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 船是我的！ - 船会撑不住{\r}\NI'll break the engine-- It's gonna tear up--
Dialogue: 0,1:48:03.69,1:48:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}抓稳{\r}\NHold on, Martin.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:19.77,1:48:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}再会吧{\r}\N# Farewell and adieu #
Dialogue: 0,1:48:22.97,1:48:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}美丽的西班牙女O{\r}\N# You fair Spanish ladies #
Dialogue: 0,1:48:27.41,1:48:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}再会吧{\r}\N# Farewell and adieu #
Dialogue: 0,1:48:29.48,1:48:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}美丽的西班牙女O{\r}\NYou ladies of Spain
Dialogue: 0,1:48:33.98,1:48:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}因为我已奉命 即将返回波士顿{\r}\NFor we received orders For to sail back to Boston
Dialogue: 0,1:48:38.96,1:48:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}白痴！你会烧坏引擎！{\r}\NYou idiot, you burned out the bearings.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:41.52,1:48:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我要下去看看{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:48:43.66,1:48:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好了，停船！{\r}\N[ Brody ] All right, stop the boat. Stop the boat ! Stop it !
Dialogue: 0,1:50:04.41,1:50:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}胡柏！{\r}\NHooper !
Dialogue: 0,1:50:06.91,1:50:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}警长{\r}\NChief.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:24.99,1:50:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}胡柏，你们带这些东西 是干什么用的？{\r}\NHooper, what exactly can you do with these things of yours ?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:33.57,1:50:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}在里面装二十CC的硝酸盐{\r}\NWell, I think I can pump 20 ccs of strychnine nitrate into him,
Dialogue: 0,1:50:38.01,1:50:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}如果靠近一点的话{\r}\Nif I can get close enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:43.28,1:50:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}就可以打进它的体内？{\r}\NCan you get this little needle through his skin ?
Dialogue: 0,1:50:47.75,1:50:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}不，我做不到{\r}\NNo, I can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:51.09,1:50:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}但如果距离够近 我想由笼子里打入它的嘴中{\r}\NBut if I can get him close enough to this cage, I could get him in the mouth.
Dialogue: 0,1:50:54.42,1:50:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 鲨会撕烂你的笼子 - 你还有更好的意见吗？{\r}\NThat shark will rip that cage -- You got any better suggestions ?
Dialogue: 0,1:51:23.65,1:51:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}- 慢点 - 慢点{\r}\NEasy, easy.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:25.35,1:51:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}竖起来{\r}\NAll right, up she goes.
Dialogue: 0,1:51:30.03,1:51:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ease her up.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:23.38,1:52:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我不用鱼枪{\r}\NI ain't got no spit.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:39.26,1:52:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}我没下去前别让它靠近{\r}\NTry and keep him off me until I'm lower.
Dialogue: 0,1:52:44.57,1:52:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}好了，我准备好了{\r}\NOkay, okay, I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:43.18,1:55:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}把他拉上来！该死！{\r}\NBring him up, goddamn it !
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.92,1:55:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}把他拉上来！{\r}\NBring him up now !
Dialogue: 0,1:55:52.69,1:55:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}拉他上来！{\r}\NPull it up ! Pull it !
Dialogue: 0,1:56:01.03,1:56:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}拉他上来！{\r}\NBring him up. What are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:04.47,1:56:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}拉他上来！拉他上来！{\r}\NCome on, Quint, bring him in.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:10.37,1:56:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}滑下去了！{\r}\NIt's giving way !
Dialogue: 0,1:56:23.79,1:56:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}拉住了吗？{\r}\NRig something. Rig something!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:29.19,1:56:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}上来了！{\r}\NGot it ? All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:30.36,1:56:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it ? All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:32.60,1:56:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}上来了{\r}\NIt's coming. Slower.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:36.27,1:56:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}慢点{\r}\NSlower!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:53.03,1:59:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}来呀，给我看钢桶{\r}\NCome on, show me the tank. Blow up !
Dialogue: 0,2:00:13.48,2:00:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}炸死你！{\r}\NBlow up !
Dialogue: 0,2:00:18.55,2:00:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs24}笑吧，你这K{\r}\NSmile, you son-of-a-bitch !
